Umubare w'abarwayi ba coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane muri EU/European Economic Area no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abanduye coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibintu bimeze kimwe mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Mu Karere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo ibipimo byagiye bitandukana bitewe n'ibihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ukurikije ubunararibonye bw'u Butaliyani, leta, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bigomba kongera imyiteguro ku buryo hazabaho kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bitaro byagutse.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari itsinda ry'abarwaye indwara ya Pneumonia y'impyiko zidakomeye, byatangajwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko umuganga utera iyi ndwara ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero ya 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa na Pneumonia cyangwa ntayo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 iragenda irushaho kuremba igasaba kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% barwara cyane bagakenera kwitabwaho mu bitaro bikomeye.
Imfu z'abarwayi bavurwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 zigera kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 yiyongera mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (UK) hanyuma tuyigereranya n'ibyabaye mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yongeye gukwirakwira mu turere twinshi kandi ingufu z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu zikurikiye ingufu z'icyorezo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru Eurosurveillance 2020 cyo ku ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari we Munyurayi wa mbere wemejweho COVID-19 hakurikijwe ibisobanuro bya WHO.
Muri EU/EEA, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (UK), hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'iya 15 Werurwe 2020 iyo tariki ikaba irimo, hari abarwayi 39,768 n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu gihe abarwayi 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441 ari abo mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona imibare yose hamwe n'ibimenyetso byose by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 buri gihugu ku isi yose ku isaha ya saa munani z'amanywa buri munsi. Iyi mibare ituruka gusa ku makuru yemewe nk'ibiro by'ubuzima by'icyo gihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'akarere, na WHO.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 iteye mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ndetse no kuyigereranya n'uko iteye mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igereranyo cy'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bariho, twabaze imibare y'ibyabaye mu minsi 14 ishize, bityo dusanga ingendo kamere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekana imibare y'abarwayi bose batangajwe n'ibihugu byose kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa, ugereranyije n'abari mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Imibare y'ibyumweru 14 by'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza muri rusange ikurikirana iy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku baturage bose bo muri EU/EEA n'ab'u Bwongereza, ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibindi bisobanuro).
Iyi mibare ahanini iterwa n'izamuka ryihuse ry'umubare w'abanduye baturuka mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekana ko habayeho kwiyongera nk'uko mu bindi bihugu (Ibindi).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Aya makuru agaragaza ko, kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari byatangaje umubare w'abanduye ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibisubizo byacu bigaragaza ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yiyongereye cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mubare w'ibyago bya COVID-19 by'ubwiyongere igaragaza ko icyorezo kiri kwiyongera ku muvuduko ugereranywa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni ibyo nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibihe bitandukanye byo kugerwaho, ibisubizo bitandukanye by'ubuzima rusange, kandi bishoboka ko hashobora kuba hari itandukaniro mu bisobanuro by'uburwayi hagati y'ibihugu ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenyekane ko barwaye COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa nyuma.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu karere k'u Butaliyani kagwiririwe n'icyorezo basobanuye ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe byo muri ako karere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru y'abemerewe COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ari ku kigero cya 6% na 1% by'abarwayi (amakuru ntaragaragazwa).
Ariko, amakuru agomba gukusanywa mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo yuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi y'ubu yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 bugaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu bijyanye no kuboneka kw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU n'iby'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze mu Burayi, kuva ku 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 ku baturage 100.000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (12.5 ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU na serivisi z'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-2011).
Ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga bijyanye n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'imibare y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bo kwa muganga muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA na UK bijyanye n'ibyago >90% byo kurenza ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya serivisi z'ubuvuzi, byatanzwe mu ivugururwa rya gatandatu ry'igeragezwa ryihuse rya ECDC ku bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bagizwe n'ibice bimwe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe bikunze gukorera abaturage bagenewe serivisi z'akarere, amakuru ku barwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe yagombye gutangwa ku rwego rw'Akarere kagenwe ku mibare 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'u Burayi n'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'iburasirazuba (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza.
Ku bw'ibyo, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi barwaye cyane bigomba kwitegura uburyo bwo guhererekanya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kongera umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bitaro bya muganga, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya ECDC riherutse gukorwa, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bwuzuye ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, hamwe no kuva ku buryo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, kuko kwiyongera vuba kw'umubare w'abanduye, nk'uko byitezwe, bishobora kutaha igihe gihagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro byo gusobanukirwa, kwakira no guhuza ibisubizo bya ngombwa niba bitakozwe mbere.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rirerekana ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari uburyo bugufi bwo kubona igihe igihugu gishobora kongera ingufu mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Iyo bitabaye ibyo, izindi gahunda z'ubuzima mu bihugu bya EU/EEA zishobora guhura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye ya 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwanduza abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, biteza amakuba ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi ihuriyeho, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwanduzwa n'ikivumbi kandi igateza ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, COVID-19 ifite igipimo cyo kugabanuka no gupfa gike ugereranyije na SARS, ariko yandura cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, ndetse no ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo by'imfashanyigisho byagiye byiyongera mu buryo bwihuse ku birebana n'iyo ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo yagerageje gutanga isuzuma ryuzuye kandi ryuzuye ku birebana n'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kigenda kigenda kivuka mu buryo bwihuse.
Tuzaganira ku by'ibanze mu by'icyorezo, etiology, virology, gusuzuma, kuvura, kubara no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hakiri ibibazo byinshi bitarasobanurwa, twizeye ko iyi raporo izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteje akaga.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye ikintu kitazibagirana kandi kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru n'ibyumweru bikurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya ya virusi.
Iyi virusi ihuriye cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; bityo, iyi virusi yahawe izina rya SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, n'indwara itera yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma abantu 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 barataha naho abagera ku 3,000 barapfa.
OMS itera inkunga ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa rubanda wa mbere" kandi ko ishobora kwangiza cyane kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yemeza urutonde rwa virusi yabonetse mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe, inyandiko zirenga 200 zanditswe kuri COVID-19, zirimo iby'ubwandu, icyorezo, etiology, gusuzuma no kuvura.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusobanura iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi muri iki gice gishya cyihuta.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, ari yo MERS, icyorezo cyo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati.
Nanone kandi, tuzasuzuma ibyo twize kugeza ubu ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kuzisuzuma, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo byinshi bidasubijwe, ariko byihutirwa.
Ubusanzwe, CoV ifatwa nk'indwara idateza urupfu ku bantu, ahanini itera nibura 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye CoV ebyiri zangiza cyane abantu, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, buri imwe yatumye habaho ibyorezo byatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze byakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite ubwandu n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1.1, icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitamenyekanye cyatangiriye kuvugwa mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 ku Kigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima cyo mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hasohotse urukurikirane rwa CoV.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, ni bwo habonetse umuntu wa mbere wapfuye ahereye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu migi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, hatanzwe amakuru y'ubwandu bw'abakozi b'ubuzima, byerekana ko ubwandu bw'abantu bushobora kubaho.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, akarere kagenzurwa mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'ingendo zose z'abantu ku giti cyabo zarahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iki cyorezo bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bagaragaweho ubwandu, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho byatekerejwe ko ari ho hatanzwe ubwandu buturutse ku matungo atazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku buzima ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyo ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo cya 2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka mu buryo bwihuse cyane, icyiciro cya nyuma n'uburemere bw'icyorezo biracyari ngombwa ko byemezwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866, bwarimo abarwayi 4,021 banduye COVID-19, bwatanze isura nshya y'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, bake bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi abantu 14 gusa banduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane abagabo (0.31/100.000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100.000).
COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu matsinda, cyane cyane muri Hubei no mu nkengero zayo.
COVID-19 itwara iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva itangiye kugeza igihe itangiye kwandura.
Igihe cy'uburumbuke kigera ku minsi 4.8.
Igihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina kuva umuntu avutse kugeza apfuye ni iminsi 9.5 (4.8-13).
Umubare w'ibanze w'ubwiyongere (R0) ni 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05) na R0 ikurikije 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, bihuye n'igihe cy'ingendo zikomeye mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Imfu z'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwemejwe ni 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%) n'imfu z'abarwayi bose ni 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi byateza COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60), na Pneumonia ikomeye.
CoV ni umuryango muto wa virusi nini zifite uruhu rwihariye zirimo urumogi rumwe rwa RNA.
CoVs zishobora kugabanywamo amoko ane, ari yo alpha, beta, gamma na delta, aho alpha na beta-CoVs bizwi ko zandura abantu.
Poroteyine ya glycoprotein cyangwa spike (S) y'umwandiko ifata ku cyuma cyakira ingirabuzima fatizo, angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE 2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) ku buryo bwa SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hanyuma membrane fusion iba.
Inkomoko ya virusi ya RNA irasohoka mu cytoplasma; nyuma yo gusubiramo genom ya virusi, RNA ya genomic iherekejwe na glycoproteins y'umwambaro na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid ihimba uduseke turimo virions, nyuma tukagira fusion n'urusobe rwa plasma kugirango dusohore virusi.
Urukurikirane rwa genomic rwa SARS-CoV-2 rwa mbere rwatangajwe ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 ni beta-CoV nshya ifite umwihariko mu binyabuzima ungana na 99,98% mu bipimo 10 byafashwe; ibi bipimo byavuye mu isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Mu buryo bw'imiterere, SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane na SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Binyuze mu gukoresha mikorosikopi ya elegitoronike, udukoko twa SARS-CoV-2 twabonetse mu gice cy'urwagashya rw'umwuka mu mwuka w'umuntu.
ACE2 mu bantu yagaragaye ari receptor ya SARS-CoV-2 kimwe na SARS-CoV.
Icyakora, poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano n'umuntu ACE2 ariko ni nke ugereranyije n'iyo SARS-CoV S, ibyo bikaba bihuje n'uko SARS-CoV-2 itatera indwara zidakomeye nk'iza SARS-CoV mu barwayi.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine nto nshya ishyizwe muri orf3b na poroteyine yihishe mu cyuma cyitwa orf8.
Poroteyine ya orf3b ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu kurwara virusi no mu kubuza IFNβ kugaragaza; ariko, orf8 nta ruhare rw'imikorere cyangwa impamvu izwi.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al. batangaje ko abantu bose bafite icyuma cya ACE2 cy'ubushakashatsi (cryo-EM) ku buryo bwa 2,9 Å mu buryo bw'amajwi (complex) hamwe n'umuvuduko wa B0AT1 mu byuma by'amino acid.
Basanze uruvange, rufite imiterere y'urufunguzo n'iy'urufunzo, rwaremwe mu buryo bwa dimer kandi uruvange rwa ACE2-B0AT1 rushobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, bikaba ari ibimenyetso byo kumenya no kwandura CoV.
B0AT1 ishobora gukoreshwa nk'intego mu kuvura imiti igabanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Nyir'ubwite n'umuhuza
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV bizwi ko byakomotse ku birura kandi buri kimwe cyandikirwa abantu binyuze mu mashyamba na za ngamiya.
Binyuze mu kugereranya kwa phylogenetic ya SARS-CoV-2 n'indi CoV, udusimba twafashwe nk'abatanga SARS-CoV-2 kuko iyi virusi nshya ihuriyeho na 96% na CoV ebyiri zisa na SARS zo mu ducurama twitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Icyakora, abarwayi ba intermédiaire bafasha virusi kwambuka inzitizi z'ubwoko kugira ngo yandure abantu ntibaramenyekana, kandi inzira y'ubwandu iracyari iyo gusobanurwa.
Ji, et al. batanga igitekerezo cy'inzoka nk'umuyoboro wa virusi uva mu birura bigera ku bantu bigatuma habaho guhuza kwa homolog mu poroteyine ya S.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, bavuga ko inguge, inyamaswa zifite amazuru maremare zirya ibiheri zikunze gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, zishobora kuba ari zo nyamaswa z'ingenzi mu gutera SARS-CoV-2 hashingiwe ku buryo 99% z'ubwoko bwa CoVs ziboneka mu nguge na SARS-CoV-2.
Nyamara, 1% y'ubundi butandukane busakaye muri uko kuboko kwa mudasobwa ni bwo butandukanye cyane; bityo rero, nta gihamya gifatika cy'uko hari ikintu runaka cyakozwe (Igishushanyo cya 3).
Imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 mu by'ukuri ntizwi.
Mu byumba, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'umwotsi n'iminsi 5 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe bwa 40%-50% na 20 °C.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite imiterere nk'iyo.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 yumva urumuri rw'umusase n'izuba ry'umuriro wa 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; eteri, 75% ya ethanol, umuti wica udukoko urimo chlorine, acide peroxyate, chloroform n'indi myunyu y'amavuta, ariko atari chlorhexidine, byangiza virusi neza.
Muri rusange, abantu bose nta bushobozi bafite bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi burambuye bwakozwe ku bisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ku bw'ibyo, dushobora gusa kwerekeza ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku zindi CoV, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo cya 4).4).
Muri rusange, nyuma yo kwigarurira umukerarugendo, virusi imenyekana n'umubiri binyuze mu byuma by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri (PRR), birimo C-type lectin-like receptor, Toll-like receptor (TLR), NOD-like receptor (NLR), na RIG-I-like receptor (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma habaho kugaragaza ibintu by'ubuhumekero, gukura kw'ingirabuzima fatizo, no gukora interféron y'ubwoko bwa I (IFN) ihagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi kandi igatuma imyanya ndangagitsina yihuta cyane.
Icyakora, poroteyine N muri SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi kwirinda ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri.
Nyuma y'igihe gito, abashinzwe kurwanya iyi virusi bahise biyunga mu kurwanya iyo virusi.
T-lymphocyte, zikubiyemo CD4+ na CD8+, zigira uruhare rukomeye muri ubu burinzi.
CD4+ T cell zitera B cell gukora antibody yihariye kuri virusi, naho CD8+ T cell zica virusi zanduye.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za T z'abafasha zitanga cytokines z'ubuhumekero kugira ngo zifashe kurinda ingirabuzimafatizo.
Icyakora, CoV ishobora kubuza T cells gukora binyuze mu gutuma T cell apoptosis iba.
Ubwugamo bw'umubiri, bukubiyemo ibyifuzo, nka C3a na C5a, hamwe n'udupira tw'amaraso na byo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa virusi.
Urugero, abasirikare barwanya virusi bakomoye ku murwayi wakize, bashobora kuvanaho MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, uburyo bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara butuma habaho ingufu nyinshi z'imikorere mibi, bishobora kwangiza cyane ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu gihe kibi cyane, bigatuma ingingo nyinshi zidakora neza ndetse n'urupfu.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, igaragazwa n'ibinyamubiri byinshi, yibasira cyane abantu bakuze bafite indwara ziterwa na yo n'abagore batwite.
Muri rusange, abantu barwaye virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubwirinzi budafite imbaraga baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura kurusha abandi.
Ikigereranyo cy'igihe cyo kubamo cya SARS-CoV-2 ni iminsi 1-14, hafi ya yose ni iminsi 3-7 hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 425 ba mbere banduye muri Wuhan.
Ariko, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 1,099 bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro kigera ku minsi 3 kandi ko kigera ku minsi 0 kugeza ku 24.
Ubushakashatsi bushya, nkuko byasobanuwe haruguru, bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro ari iminsi 4.8 (3.0-7.2) hashingiwe ku mubare w'abantu 8,866.
Ni ngombwa ko inzego z'ubuzima zihindura igihe cy'ikurwa mu kato gikwiye hashingiwe ku gihe cy'igwingira gihagije kugira ngo abantu banduye ariko badafite ibimenyetso batanduza abandi.
Ubusanzwe, umuntu wahuye n'ubwandu cyangwa ubwandu bw'iyi virusi aba agomba kumara iminsi 14 mu kato.
