Inzara ikunze kuba ari ibimenyetso by'ibanze bya COVID-19, hamwe cyangwa bidaherekejwe n'ibindi bimenyetso nk'umuhogo utose, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'umusatsi, ibihaha, umutwe, kubabara mu muhogo, impumuro mbi, ububabare bwo mu gatuza, iseseme, kugira inyota no gusubiranamo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaza umwuka uhuha kandi/cyangwa hypoxemia nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe batangiye uburwayi.
Mu bihe bikomeye, indwara y'umurwayi igenda yihuta igatera indwara y'ubuhumekero, sepsis, acidosis ya metabolic na coagulopathy.
Abarwayi bagaragaza umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukabije, nubwo nta ndwara zo mu bihaha, bagomba gukorerwa isuzuma ry'ubwandu bwa virusi kugira ngo bagaragazwe hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku baturage mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'indwara ari 98% ku ndwara y'umuriro, 76% ku iseru ryumye, 55% ku ndwara ya dyspnea, na 3% ku ndwara ya diarrhée; 8% by'abarwayi bakeneye inkunga y'umuyoboro wa Ventilator.
Ibisubizo nk'ibyo byatangajwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa, ubushakashatsi ku muryango n'ubw'abantu batandura.
Mu buryo buhabanye n'ubwo, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV na bo bagaragazaga umuriro (98%), inkorora yumye (47%), na dyspnea (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi.
Icyakora, 80% by'abarwayi bakeneye inkunga yo guhumeka, ari benshi cyane kurusha abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi bihuje n'uko MERS ihitana benshi kurusha COVID-19.
Kurwara ibicurane (26%) no kuribwa mu muhogo (21%) nabyo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora yumye (29%-75%), guhumeka (40%-42%), iseseme (20-25%), no kuribwa mu muhogo (13-25%) byerekanwe nk'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi kandi inkunga y'umwuka ikenewe mu barwayi bagera kuri 14%-20%.
