Mu buryo buhabanye n'ubwo, umubare w'abapfa kubera SARS mu Gushyingo 2002 wari 10% ku bantu 8,096 bamaze kwemezwa.
Ku bijyanye na MERS, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa Kamena 2012, umubare w'abapfa ni 37% mu bantu 2,494 bamaze kwemezwa.
