Ubumuga bwo mu gatuza bw'amafoto buboneka mu barwayi benshi ba COVID-19 kandi bugaragazwa n'igicucu cy'ibicu bibiri cyangwa ubumuga bw'ibihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira indwara y'ibihaha, ubumuga bwo mu bihaha no kurwara indwara y'ubuhumekero (ARDS).
Iyo ARDS ibayeho, ubuhumekero budategekanywa, kwiyongera kw'amazi n'imiterere y'umubiri bigenda birushaho gutuma habaho ibibazo byo guhanahana ibyuka.
Imikorere mibi y'utugingo tw'amaraso tw'ubwoko bwa I n'ubw'ubwoko bwa II, ituma habaho kugabanuka kw'imikorere y'utugingo tw'amaraso n'umuvuduko w'amaraso, bityo bigatuma ibihaha bidashobora kwaguka kandi bigatuma ibyago byo kwandura by'ibihaha byiyongera.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, ibipimo bibi cyane ku mashusho y'igituza akenshi bijyana n'ubukana bw'indwara.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryerekanye ko mu bihaha by'abarwayi bapfuye, habayeho gusama kw'udutsi tw'amaraso, habaho gushinga udutsi tw'amaraso tw'amaraso, habaho no kwinjira kw'udutsi tw'amaraso tw'amaraso, ndetse n'udutsi tw'amaraso tw'amaraso tw'amaraso tw'abantu benshi bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara, ibyo bikaba bihuye n'indwara z'ubwandu bwa virusi na ARDS ndetse n'isesengura ry'indwara nk'izo mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kumenya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu buryo bwa RT-PCR (reverse transcriptase polymerase chain reaction) ni byo by'ingenzi mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Ariko kubera ko ibipimo byinshi by'ibinyoma by'ibinyoma, bishobora kwihutisha icyorezo, ibimenyetso by'inzobere byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma (bitagishingiye gusa kuri RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu bisa n'ibyo kandi ni ko bimeze ku barwayi ba SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhuza amateka y'uburwayi, ibimenyetso byo mu bitaro, ibizamini byo mu bitaro n'ibisubizo bya radiyoloji ni iby'ingenzi cyane kandi ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona indwara neza.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye gahunda yo gukoresha ubuhanga bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, bwasuzumye ibice bya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 ikorwa mu 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kopi kuri microlitiro y'ibikoresho) hakoreshejwe inkoni yo kwibiza mu gihe kitarenze isaha idafite ibikoresho bihambaye.
Twizeye ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ubudahangarwa n'ubworoherane mu gihe bwaba bwemejwe mu bipimo byo mu buvuzi.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye kuri CoV nshya, abaganga ahanini batanga ubuvuzi bw'inkunga ku barwayi ba COVID-19, mu gihe bagerageza uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mbere yo kuvura izindi CoV, nka SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe ya 2).2.
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura burimo uburyo bwo kuvura buriho n'ubushobozi bwo kuvura bufite imiti ya virusi, imyunyo itera indwara z'umubiri, siteroyi, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa, n'ubufasha bwo mu mutwe.
Ndetse n'umushongi w'amaraso uturuka ku barwayi bakize, wateganyijwe gukoreshwa mu buvuzi.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi arimo arashakisha uburyo bwo kuvura iyo virusi.
Mu byiciro bya mbere, SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane ibihaha kandi ishobora no gutera izindi ngingo zivuga ACE2 ku kigero cyo hasi, nk'urwungano rw'amaraso n'impyiko.
Ariko kandi, guhumeka nabi no kunanirwa guhumeka ni byo bintu by'ingenzi bibangamiye abarwayi kandi ni byo bituma abantu benshi bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, inkunga yo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima, ikubiyemo uburyo rusange bwo guhumeka, umwuka uhagije, guhumeka ku buryo butari ubusanzwe, no guhumeka ku buryo bw'imashini, bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba gushyigikirwa na oxygénation membrane extracorporeum (ECMO), ni uburyo bwo guhitamo uburyo bwo guhumeka bw'umutima bukoreshwa mu kuvura umutima udakora neza cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Byongeye kandi, kwita ku rugero rwa electrolyte, kwirinda no kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero n'imiterere y'imyanda, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ingenzi ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Igisubizo cy'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara bizwi ko gitera ibiza bya sitokine mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Cytokine cyst ni uburyo bw'igisubizo cy'ubuhumekero bw'umubiri bugaragazwa no kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibikoresho bya cytokine, birimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytokines zitera ingirabuzima fatizo z'umubiri kurekura ingano nini y'imikorere mibi y'imikorere mibi, ari nayo mpamvu nyamukuru y'indwara ya ARDS n'imikorere mibi y'ingingo.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi mu guhangana n'ibiza bya cytokine, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukabije.
Korticosteroids na Tocilizumab, umuti wa monoclonal anti-IL6, byakoreshejwe mu guhangana n'ibiza bya sitokine.
Ubundi buryo bwo kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'imyakura ya sitokine burimo uburyo bwo guhindura ibisubizo by'umubiri bigenzurwa na T-cell; guhagarika IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK; blinatumomab; guhagarika ibimenyetso bya sitokine 4; no kubuza HDAC.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, ikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse by'ubuhumekero.
Icyakora, gukoresha ibipimo byinshi bya siteroide nta cyo byamara mu kuvura ibikomere bikomeye by'ibihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, siteroyi ishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye, cyane cyane osteonecrosis, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku ndwara.
Icyakora, gutanga corticosteroids mu gihe gito ku gipimo cyo hasi cyane, byasabwaga ko bitangwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane.
Mu gihe cyo kwandika iyi raporo, nta miti ya virusi ifite ubushobozi bwemewe.
Icyakora, imiti ya remdesivir, ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara ya COVID-19 muri Amerika, yagaragaye ko ifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura indwara.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya wa virusi wakozwe na Gilead, watangiriye mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma, remdesivir yagaragaje kandi kubuza izindi virusi za RNA z'uruhu rumwe, zirimo virusi ya MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibyo, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uru ruganda kugira ngo rukore igerageza ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin byatanzwe nk'uburyo bushobora kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Kurwara ibicurane, iseseme, gusubiranamo, kwangirika kw'umutima, n'ibindi bibazo bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufata imiti ivanze na lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Ibi bikorwa by'ubuvuzi hamwe n'indi miti umurwayi akoresha bigomba gukurikiranwa cyane.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'imikorere y'abanduye
Hari amateka maremare yo gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara zandura kugira ngo bavurwe abandi barwayi bafite indwara imwe cyangwa kugira ngo barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwandura izo ndwara.
Ni iby'ukuri ko abarwayi bakize akenshi bagira ibipimo by'amaraso bifite abasirikare b'umubiri benshi.
Umubiri ni umuti witwa immunoglobuline (Ig) utangwa na za globule B kugira ngo urwanye indwara n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga, umenye molekile zihariye mu ndwara, kandi uzihashye.
Bishingiye kuri ibi, plasma yakusanyijwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bayitera abarwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagabanutse mu masaha 24, biherekejwe no kugabanuka kw'imyidodombo n'umutwaro wa virusi ndetse n'izamuka ry'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko, igenzura no gusobanura birakenewe kugirango uburyo bushobore gukoreshwa cyane mbere yuko uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura butangira.
Byongeye kandi, uretse ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari ibindi bintu bike cyane bifitanye isano na plasma bigomba kwitabwaho.
Urugero, abarwayi bashobora gukabya gutera ingufu umubiri wabo mu kurwanya indwara, bigatuma habaho indwara y'imyanda ifata imyakura (syndrome de libération de cytokines), ishobora gushyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Umubare w'abanduye mu maraso ubusanzwe uba uri hasi, kandi mu gihe umuntu arwaye cyane, hakenerwa amaraso menshi.
Gutegura no gukora antibody yihariye mu buryo bwihuse ku buryo bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cy'isi biragoye.
Niyo mpamvu ari ingenzi kandi byoroshye cyane gutandukanya uturemangingo twa B mu barwayi bakize no kumenya kode y'imiterere y'utwo turemangingo, kugira ngo dushobore gutandukanya utwo turemangingo n'utundi turemangingo duto cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera mu buryo bworoshye umubare w'abanduye.
Umuco wa TCM wakoreshejwe mu buvuzi bw'indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi.
Ariko ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingira ku miterere y'ibice bitandukanye biri muri formula.
Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bifite akamaro biracyari ibyigaragaza cyangwa bidafite ishingiro kubera ko bigoye kubikuramo cyangwa kubisobanura cyangwa se kubikoresha mu buryo bwiza.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ko nta miti yihariye kandi ikora neza ya COVID-19 ikiriho, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti y'ingenzi ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa ku bantu bakize indwara ikomeye.
Urugero, ingunguru ya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen zagize ingaruka nziza mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byo kugabanuka kw'indwara muri gahunda yo kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19 byagaragariye mu ntara zimwe na zimwe z'Ubushinwa zikoresha TCM ku barwayi 87% barimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei ikoresha TCM ku barwayi 30% gusa ba COVID-19, ifite igipimo cyo kugabanuka cyane (13%).
Ariko kandi, iryo gereranya riracyari ribi cyane kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka, nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere, bigomba kujyanwa mu igenzura.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye inyigo yagereranyije uburyo bwo kuvura bw'imiti yo mu Burengerazuba (WM) bwonyine n'uburyo bwo kuvura buhuriweho na WM na TCM.
Babonye ko igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, guhosha ibimenyetso no kujya mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa.
Igishishikaje kurushaho, ni uko imibare y'ibyago byo kuremba (kuva ku muvuduko woroshye kugeza ku mwinshi) yari iri hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'iryo muri WM gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%) kandi n'imfu zari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'iryo muri WM gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Nyamara, ubudahangarwa n'umutekano wa TCM biracyategereje igeragezwa rifite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura neza ku kigero kinini no mu bigo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi.
Ikindi kintu gishishikaje ni ugusobanura uburyo ikora no gusobanura neza ibice by'ingirakamaro mu buvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa mu buryo bufatika, niba bishoboka.
Abenshi mu barwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19 bafite ubwoba bw'iyi ndwara yandura cyane kandi ishobora no kwica, kandi abantu bari mu kato na bo bumva bananiwe, bafite irungu n'umujinya.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'indwara nk'umuriro, hypoxia, no gukorora hamwe n'ingaruka z'ubuvuzi nk'ibitotsi biterwa na corticosteroids bishobora gutera guhangayika no guhangayika cyane.
Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cya SARS, hari amakuru y'ubwandu bwinshi bwo mu mutwe, burimo kwiheba, guhangayika, kwiheba, guhungabana mu mitekerereze, ibimenyetso byo kwiheba, ubwirasi, ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana amateka y'abamenyanye n'abandi no guhagarika abantu mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, nk'igice cy'igisubizo cy'ubuzima rusange ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kwicira urubanza ku ngaruka z'ubwandu, guhagarika abantu mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko no gutesha agaciro bene wabo n'incuti.
Ku bw'ibyo, ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe bugomba gutangwa ku barwayi ba COVID-19, abakekwaho iyo ndwara n'ababa bahuye na bo, ndetse n'abaturage muri rusange babukeneye.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho itsinda ry'indwara zo mu mutwe, itumanaho ryiza rifite amakuru y'igihe cyose kandi y'ukuri ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, no gutegura uburyo bwo kuvurwa no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'ibikoresho by'abahanga mu kwirinda guhura cyane.
Inkingo nziza ni ingenzi mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara y'ibimera n'abantu ku bantu bafite ubwandu kandi akenshi iba iherekeje imiti ya virusi mu kugenzura icyorezo cyatewe n'ubwandu.
Hakozwe ibishoboka byose kugira ngo hatangwe urukingo rushingiye kuri poroteyine ya S, rushobora mu gihe kirekire kandi mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza, rugatuma habaho abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV.
Ku bw'indwara ya SARS, urukingo rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'umubiri rwasuzumwe mu nyamaswa.
Icyakora, ubushobozi bwa in vivo bw'urukingo mu bantu bakuze n'uburyo bwo guhangana n'indwara z'ubwandu bw'ibinyamaswa ndetse n'ubwirinzi ku ndwara ziterwa na virusi z'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa, biracyari ngombwa ko byemezwa mbere y'uko ikigo gitangira gukora ubushakashatsi.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS yashize mu myaka 17 ishize kandi nta muntu mushya wigeze avurwa kuva icyo gihe.
Ku rundi ruhande, hari abantu bake cyane kandi benshi muri bo bakomeje kwandura MERS mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, kandi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu tundi duce bitewe n'uko hari ibyago by'ubwandu bw'inyamaswa mu duce tw'aho yanduriye.
Uburyo bwo gukingira bwagiye butangizwa kuri MERS bukoresheje virusi yahagaritswe, plasmid ya ADN, virusi y'indwara, utuntu duto duto, udukoko tumeze nk'indwara, n'uduporotine duto tw'indwara z'ubuhumekero kandi bimwe byagiye bigenzurwa mu nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2 rwiza kandi rwiza ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kugenzura icyorezo gikomeje.
Icyakora, ibyo bibazo ntibyoroshye kubikemura kubera igihe kirekire cyo gukora urukingo (ku kigereranyo cy'amezi 18) n'ubwoko bw'indwara za CoV.
Kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, yatangiye kugaragaza uburwayi bwayo mu buryo bwuzuye mu barwayi ibihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, umurwayi ashobora kugenda akira nta ngaruka.
Icyakora, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 nayo ifitanye isano n'ubwandu n'urupfu mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukabije.
Ku bw'ibyo, gushinga uburyo bwo kwitegereza indwara ni ingenzi cyane ku bigo by'ubuzima kugira ngo bishyire imbere serivisi zabyo, cyane cyane mu duce dufite amikoro make.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buvuzi bwamaze gutangazwa, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bifitanye isano n'ubwiru bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe ya 3):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni cyo kintu cy'ingenzi cyane mu kwemeza ko SARS izaza, nk'uko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane cyane abantu bafite hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65 aho 47,7% by'abarwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwari bufite abarwayi 8,866 nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye bakunze kugira indwara ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'indwara hamwe n'ibibazo kandi bafite imyaka myinshi ugereranyije n'abatarakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye (imyaka yo hagati ni 66 ugereranyije na 51), ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko imyaka ari ingenzi mu kugaragaza ingaruka z'abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore (0.31/100.000 ugereranyije na 0.27/100.000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi n'ibibazo: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane barushaho kurwara umutima cyane no kugira arrhythmie.
Ibyago by'umutima kandi ni yo mpamvu nyamukuru y'urupfu mu barwayi ba SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza na cholangiocytes zifite ACE2-zishimishije, bishobora gutera indwara y'umwijima mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni iby'ingenzi kuzirikana ko imyaka n'uburwayi byombi bifitanye isano kandi ko bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bandi.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe byo mu bitaro: Ibipimo bya poroteyine ya C-reactive (CRP) mu maraso bigaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa imvune mu mitsi kandi byatangijwe nk'ikintu gishobora kwemeza indwara, gusubiza imiti no gukira.
Hatanzwe kandi ibisobanuro ku bijyanye n'ihura hagati y'ibipimo bya CRP n'uburemere n'ubwirinzi bwa COVID-19.
Byongeye kandi, kuzamuka kwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu kwemeza ibisubizo bya nyuma.
Izi enzymes zivugwa cyane mu ngingo zitandukanye, cyane cyane mu mutima n'igifu, kandi zisohoka mu gihe habaye imyanda.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, izo enzymes ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'imikorere mibi y'umutima n'ibindi.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi: Ifoto y'igituza n'imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi mu gihe cy'igihe bigomba gusuzumwa hamwe n'ibindi kugira ngo hategerezwe ingaruka n'ibibazo bya COVID-19.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids ni imiti yica abarwayi ikoreshwa cyane nk'ubuvuzi bw'inkunga ku ndwara z'ubwandu mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse.
Kubera ko ibipimo byinshi bya corticosteroids bikoreshwa cyane mu barwayi ba SARS ikomeye, abantu benshi barokotse iyi ndwara amaherezo barwara osteonecrosis avascular ibaviramo ubumuga ubuzima bwabo bwose n'ubuzima bubi.
Ku bw'ibyo, niba ari ngombwa, siteroyi zigomba gukoreshwa mu buryo buciriritse kandi ku gipimo cyo hasi mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Imihangayiko yo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bahanganye n'imihangayiko idasanzwe kubera ko baba bagomba kumara igihe kirekire mu kato kandi bafite impungenge zikomeye ndetse no kwibonera urupfu rw'abagize umuryango wabo na bagenzi babo.
Inama z'imitekerereze n'ubufasha bw'igihe kirekire bigomba gutangwa kugira ngo bifashe uyu murwayi gukira imihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mibare y'abaturage kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n'ifite icyerekezo cy'icyorezo gitandukanye na SARS.
Uretse kwanduza mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduza neza mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru kandi igateza ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'ibanze, kimwe n'indi mikorobe zitera ibicurane.
Ku bw'ibyo, mu gihe cy'intangiriro cyangwa igihe cyo kubamo, abarwayi banduye bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu bikorwa byabo bya buri munsi, bigatuma bigorana cyane kugenzura icyorezo.
Icyakora, SARS-CoV yemerwa ko yandura iyo umurwayi arwaye cyane kandi akenshi ntiyigera yandura mu bihe bya mbere.
Bityo rero, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi kiragoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe, mu Bushinwa hari imbaraga zikomeye zirimo gukorwa, zirimo gushyira mu kato akarere ka Wuhan n'imidugudu ihakikije ndetse no gushyira mu kato abaturage hafi ya bose mu rwego rwo kwizeza ko hagiye guhagarara ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibi byahungabanyije cyane ubukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya waragabanutse, byerekana ko icyorezo cyaragabanutse.
Impinduka nziza cyane ni uko icyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, maze icyiciro cyo kugabanuka kikazamara amezi atatu cyangwa ane.
Icyakora, hari abandi bahanga batagira icyizere nk'icyo.
Paul Hunter et al. batanga icyizere ko COVID-19, isa n'iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu mwaka wa 2020.
Ira Longini, et al. bakoze icyitegererezo cyo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo kandi bavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kanada batangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu muhogo no mu muhogo w'abarwayi bakize bagasohoka ibitaro mu byumweru bibiri bishize, byerekana ko virusi yongeye kumenyekana ishobora kuba ari icyorezo gisubirwamo, gisa n'icy'ibicurane.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko mu Bushinwa hari icyizere, iyo urebye kugabanuka kw'umubare w'abandura bashya, bigaragaza ko ingamba z'ubu zishobora kugira icyo zigeraho.
Ebola yari yitezweho ko izateza abantu bagera kuri miliyoni imwe, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bakaba ari bo bapfa.
Ariko kandi, hamwe no gushyirwa mu kato no kwigunga bikomeye, iyi ndwara amaherezo ishobora kugenzurwa.
Birashoboka kandi ko kimwe na SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 yagabanyije ubushobozi bwayo bwo kwanduza, amaherezo irazimira cyangwa ikaba virusi idashobora gutera indwara cyane ishobora guhura n'abantu.
Gereranya icyorezo cya COVID-19 n'icyorezo cya SARS na MERS bitangwa hepfo (Igishushanyo cya 5).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura mu buryo bworoshye binyuze mu gukorora cyangwa gutera akabariro, kandi bishobora no guterwa no guhura n'ikintu cyafashwe na virusi.
Iyi virusi kandi iboneka mu binyamubiri bituma habaho uburyo bushya bwo kuyikwirakwiza, ari bwo kwikwirakwiza mu binyamubiri binyuze mu kanwa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abo barwayi bashobora kuba barwaye indwara ziterwa n'imyanya ndangagitsina, aho abarwaye 17 bari bafite izindi ndwara n'abakozi 40 b'ubuzima.
Ku bw'ibyo, ingamba z'ubwirinzi zikwiye gufatwa kugira ngo abantu barinde, cyane cyane abashinzwe ubuzima, abakozi bashinzwe imibereho myiza y'abaturage, abagize umuryango, abo bakorana ndetse n'abantu bahura n'abarwayi cyangwa abanduye.
Urukuta rwa mbere rw'ingabo rushobora gukoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ugukoresha udupfukamunwa, tw'imiti n'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi (masque chirurgical) n'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero twitwa N95 (numero z'ingingo zo mu 1860s) dufasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turinda amacandwe y'umuntu ushobora kwandura guhita agera mu kirere cyangwa kumeneka ku bintu, aho ashobora gukwirakwira ku bandi.
Ariko, gusa udupfukamunwa twa N95 (nomero y'uruhererekane 1860s) ni two dushobora kurinda umuntu guhumeka virions z'ubunini buto cyane bwa 10 kugeza kuri 80 nm, aho 5% gusa bya virions ari byo byonyine bishobora kwinjira burundu; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini, byombi bikaba bigera kuri 85 nm.
Kubera ko udusate dushobora kwinjira no mu masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi ziteretse hamwe, abavura bahura n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara N95 (umubare w'ingingo 1860s) aho kwambara masike z'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abashinzwe ubuzima bagomba kwambara imyenda ikwiriye yo kwicungira mu buryo bw'umubiri kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya guhura na virusi.
Virusi ishobora no kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu gucurama kw'ijisho.
Ku bw'ibyo, abavura abaganga bagomba no kwambara udukingirizo tw'amaso cyangwa uturore mu gihe bakorana n'umurwayi.
Ku baturage muri rusange bari mu duce twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, birasabwa cyane ko buri wese yoza intoki ze akoresheje isabune yica udukoko kenshi, akagerageza kuguma mu rugo mu rwego rwo kwisanzura, kandi akirinda guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Kuba umuntu ataramana n'undi n'ibirenge bitatu, ni byiza kugira ngo umurwayi agume kure ye.
Ibyo bikorwa ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi nshya ku bantu, kuba ifite aho ihuriye na SARS-CoV, nk'uko byatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, byagombye kuba umuburo ukomeye ku Bushinwa bufite kwibuka cyane icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003.
Nyamara, ku ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya indwara yahumurije abaturage avuga ko iyi virusi nshya ifite ubukana buciriritse kandi ubushobozi bwo kwanduzanya buciriritse kuva ku muntu ujya ku wundi kandi kwirinda no gukumira iyi ndwara ntabwo ari ikibazo.
Ubwo butumwa bwateye ubwoba abaturage cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari kigiye kwitegura Umunsi Mukuru w'Igisibo, bityo igihe gikomeye cyo guhashya icyorezo cy'indwara kiri mu mujyi wa Wuhan kikaba cyaratinze.
Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya indwara kigomba kuba cyarigiye ku byabaye, kandi kikagira icyo gikora kugira ngo kizahindure ibintu mu buryo bukomeye mu gihe kiri imbere.
Urugero, iyi nzego yagombye (1) kugira amakenga mu gihe itanga itanga itangazo ku mugaragaro kuko ijambo ryose rifatwaho ijisho n'abaturage kandi rishobora guhindura imyumvire n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kuba umuntu usobanukiwe kandi ugira icyo akora ku makuru adasanzwe aturuka mu bitaro aho gutegereza raporo yemewe y'abaganga cyangwa abakozi bafite ububasha; (3) kuba umuntu uhanagura ibintu byinshi kugira ngo ahagarike icyorezo mu gihe cy'ibanze, aho kugerageza guhumuriza abantu; kandi (4) kujya atanga imyitozo igamije guteza imbere abaturage no kongera ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'icyorezo kandi agakora igerageza no kongera uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye gukwirakwira mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, icyorezo cyamaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu bisaga 50 ku isi mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga.
Kubera ko iyi virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 na SARS bikaba bisa, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gisa n'icyorezo cya SARS cyongeye kugaruka.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rigaragara hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari na ryo rikomeye mu kurwanya icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato kandi yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi umubare w'abapfa na wo uri hejuru cyane mu bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato.
Imfu ziterwa na SARS ziruta iziterwa na COVID-19 (10,91% ugereranyije na 1,44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 batanga virusi nubwo nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS ubusanzwe batanga virusi iyo barwaye cyane. Ibi bituma bigoye cyane kugabanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 ugereranyije na SARS.
Ibi bisobanuye bimwe mu byatumye SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira vuba kandi mu buryo bwagutse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ibizamini bya RNA bisanzwe bigenzura SARS-CoV-2 bishobora gutanga umusaruro utaboneye mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kugaragaza virusi.
Ibi byavumbuwe byongereye cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Kubera ko ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 bugenda bufata indi ntera, hari ibibazo bikomeye bikeneye gukemurwa:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo twabonye ko SARS-CoV-2 ihuriyeho mu binyabuzima ku kigero cya 96% n'izindi virusi ebyiri zisa na SARS zo mu birura, ntitwabasha kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku birura.
Ni izihe nyamaswa zigize intermédiaire mu kwanduza abantu virusi zivuye ku nyamaswa zibarirwa mu bihumbi, urugero nk'ikinyugunyugu?
Tudafite ibisubizo bya mbere n'ibya kabiri, ntidushobora guhagarika ubwandu mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza kandi icyorezo gishobora kongera kwaduka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Nubwo imiterere ya molekile n'ibinyabuzima byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero igatuma habaho impinduka mu mikorere?
Ese iyi virusi ishobora no guhuza n'utundi turemangingo tuvuga ACE2 mu bindi bice by'umubiri?
Turamutse tudafite ibisubizo byumvikana kuri ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kugera ku bushakashatsi bwihuse kandi bw'ukuri, kandi ntidushobora no kwivuza neza.
Iki cyorezo kizakomeza kubaho igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ikura mu buryo bw'imiterere mu gihe cyo kwanduzanya hagati y'abantu?
Ese iyi ndwara izagera aho ibe icyorezo ku isi hose, ikarangira nka SARS, cyangwa igatangira kugaruka buri gihe nk'ibicurane?
Igisubizo cy'icyo kibazo n'ibindi byinshi ni ingenzi, ariko bishobora gufata igihe kugira ngo tukibone.
Ariko kandi, uko byagenda kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba uko bishoboka kose kugira ngo dushobore gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Inkomoko ya virusi ya coronavirusi y'umuntu
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, ihinduka ry'imiterere n'imiterere y'ibintu byagiye bituma koronavirusi (CoV) n'imiterere y'imiterere yayo, harimo n'abantu, bigenda bihinduka.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri banduye virusi itera SIDA (HCoV) bari bazwiho gutera indwara z'ubwoko bworoheje, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS na MERS byahinduye ibintu, byerekana ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kwangiza no guhitana ubuzima.
Igiterwa cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 cyongeye kugaragara cyane kandi gitungura abantu kubera ubwandu bwayo bwinshi, ariko n'ubwandu buciriritse ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Ku bw'ibyo, gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bizadufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka mu birura. Muri ibyo biremwa, virusi ntabwo ari indwara.
Hari kandi n'izindi HCoVs z'ibanze zizwiho kuba ari ba nyirazo.
Kumenya inyamaswa z'inyamaswa bifite ingaruka ku burinzi bw'indwara z'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire ya CoV-host mu nyamaswa bushobora no gutanga ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku ndwara ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi raporo, twerekanye uko ubumenyi dufite kuri HCoVs zirindwi bumeze, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwazo n'inkomoko yazo n'ubwandu bwazo hagati y'ubwoko.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko twagereranyije kandi dusobanura izo HCoVs mu buryo bw'ubwihindurize no kongera guhuza ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kiri kuvugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa mu guhinduranya nyir'ubwite neza n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika rya virusi ku buremere bw'indwara na byo byashyizwe ahagaragara.
Virusi ya corona (CoV) ni imwe mu zo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'ubwoko bumwe bw'indwara z'agakoko kitwa RNA, z'ubwoko bumwe, z'ubwoko bumwe.
Iyi virusi ifite genom nini cyane iri hagati ya kilobase 26 na 32 mu virusi za RNA zitwa "CoV", kubera imiterere yayo isa n'iy'ingori munsi ya mikorosikopi ya électron.
Ku bw'imiterere yayo, CoV ifite genomes zitari zisanzwe zifite imiterere isa.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome bigizwe n'ibice bibiri binini by'ibisenge by'ibitabo bifunze (ORF1a na ORF1b) bisimburana.
Poroteyine nyinshi z'ibinyabuzima zisubizwaho mu buryo bw'imikorere kugira ngo zigire poroteyine 16 zitari mu rwego rw'imiterere, zitwa nsp1~16.
Ibisigaye bya genome bigizwe n'urwego rw'ibanze rw'ibanze rw'ibanze (ORF) rw'ibinyabuzima by'ubwoko bw'imiterere, birimo udutambaro (S), udupfukamunwa (E), udutambaro (M), na nucleoproteins (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'inyongera zihariye ku bwoko runaka bwa CoV na zo zashyizwe mu mubare w'abantu bafite ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro ry'imiterere ya poroteyine, CoVs zigizwe n'imiryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, na delta-CoV); muri iyo miryango ine, beta-CoVs ni yo ifite umubare munini wa HCoVs kandi igabanywa mu miryango ine (A, B, C, na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udusimba n'udukoko duto duto ari byo bitanga ingirabuzima fatizo nyinshi za alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe ibyonnyi ari byo bitanga isoko y'ibanze ya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kunyura mu nzitizi z'ubwoko, kandi zimwe muri zo zabaye indwara z'ingenzi mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi banduye koronavirusi (HCoV).
Muri izo virusi ndwi, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoVs.
Izindi koronavirusi eshanu za beta zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, virusi ya coronavirusi y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS-CoV), virusi ya coronavirusi y'indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV), na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'imbeho na/cyangwa iseseme.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ni indwara zandura cyane, zitera indwara z'ubuhumekero bw'ibanze mu barwayi benshi kandi zigira amahirwe menshi yo gutera indwara z'ubuhumekero bukabije (ARDS) no kugaragaza mu bindi bice by'ibihaha.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwadukuwe mu mwenge w'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwashyizwe hamwe binyuze mu kwiga byimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byo kwivuza.
Mu by'ukuri, byari byemewe ko indwara ziterwa na HCoV muri rusange nta cyo zitwaye, kugeza igihe SARS yadutse.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo byangiza cyane mu mateka y'iki gihe, cyanduje abantu barenga 8,000 n'umubare w'abapfa ungana na 10%.
Hashize imyaka icumi nyuma y'aho, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) cyatumye haba icyorezo gikomeje mu Burasirazuba bwa Arabiya, ariko kigenda kiza mu bindi bice by'isi.
HCoV nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV), ikomeza kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo ntandaro y'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw'abantu barenga 3,120 no kwanduza abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Impungenge zirakomeye kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiri hafi kuza.
Izo HCoV uko ari ndwi zose zaturutse ku biremwa byo mu bwoko bwa zoonotic, urugero nk'imbeba, imbeba cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Ibihamya byinshi bishyigikira ko HCoVs zose zakomotse ku birura. Mu birura, CoV ziraryana neza kandi ntizirwara indwara, ariko zigaragaza amoko menshi y'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyabaye ingorabahizi ikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho myiza n'imyitwarire y'abantu mu Bushinwa no ku isi yose.
Kurondora inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bitanga urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka kamere, imbaraga zituma habaho, n'ibikumira kwimuka hagati y'ibinyabuzima.
Ubu bushakashatsi bushobora no kuyobora cyangwa koroshya gushakisha inyamaswa z'abashyitsi, abahuza, n'abazamura SARS-CoV-2, bifite ibisobanuro by'ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi raporo, twerekanye inkomoko ya zoonotic, ubwandu bw'ubwoko butandukanye, n'imiterere ya HCoV.
Twagaragaje kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange y'uko virusi z'inkoko za HCoV zisanzwe zitagira ubwandu mu bubiko bwazo, ariko zikaba zigize ubwandu nyuma yo kwanduzanya hagati y'ubwoko ku nyamaswa nshya.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye uko HCoV zagiye zihinduka, tubona ko ubukana bwazo bwiyongera kandi ko akenshi zituma indwara zidakwirakwira.
Ibyavuye mu cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 na byo byavuzwe muri iyi nkuru.
CoV zo mu nyamaswa zari zizwi kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1930.
Mbere y'uko HCoV-229E ya mbere ya B814 ivumburwa mu mwenge w'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane, hari ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV bwari bwaravumbuwe mu matungo yanduye, arimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, HCoVs zirindwi zagiye zishyirwa ahagaragara.
Isesengura rigufi ry'amateka y'ubushakashatsi bwa HCoV mu buryo bw'igihe (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) ni ikimenyetso cy'ubumenyi.
Iseru ya HCoV-229E yabanje gutandukanywa n'imyuka y'abafite ubwandu bw'imyuka yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru mu 1966, nyuma igahindurirwa imiterere kugira ngo itere imbere mu nkingi z'amaraso ya WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ibicurane, birimo umutwe, gutera ikiniga, kubura imbaraga no kubabara mu muhogo, biherekejwe n'umuriro n'ikoni bigaragara mu bantu 10~20% by'abafata iyo ndwara.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavuye mu mibiri y'abantu n'inzira z'uruhererekane mu bwonko bw'abana b'impanga.
Imiterere y'uburwayi bwa HCoV-OC43 isa n'iy'uburwayi buterwa na HCoV-229E, butandukanye mu bimenyetso n'ubundi burwayi bw'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka virusi ya grippe A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 zisanzwe mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi kandi zigenda zikwirakwizwa cyane mu gihe cy'itumba mu turere dufite ikirere cyiza.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cy'izo virusi zombi kiri munsi y'icyumweru kimwe, gikurikirwa n'igihe cy'uburwayi cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abakorerabushake mu bantu, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E barwaye ibicurane byoroheje.
Abarwayi bake cyane bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri budafite imbaraga bagaragaza ko bafite ubwandu bw'umuhogo.
SARS, izwi kandi nka "pneumonia atypical", ni icyorezo cya mbere cyatewe na HCoVs cyanditswe neza mu mateka y'abantu kandi intandaro yacyo ni SARS-CoV, ikaba ari HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe.
Umuntu wa mbere w'indwara ya SARS ashobora kuba yaratewe n'impeshyi yo mu 2002 mu Ntara ya Guangdong, mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje ubwandu 8,096 n'urupfu 774, mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse kuba ari indwara yandura cyane, buri murwayi ashobora gutera izindi ebyiri, mu gihe igihe cyo kubamo kiri hagati y'iminsi 4 na 7 kandi umuriro wa virusi ugaragara ku munsi wa 10.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV batangira kugaragaza uburwayi bwo mu bwonko, umutwe, umuriro, kubura imbaraga no guhinda umushyitsi, bikurikirwa no guhumeka nabi, inkorora no guhumeka nabi nk'ibimenyetso by'indwara z'uburwayi.
Imyitozo yo mu mubiri, imikorere mibi y'umwijima, no kwiyongera kwa creatine kinase ni bimwe mu bintu bikunze kugaragara mu mavuriro ya SARS.
Kuvunika kwa alveolar diffusion, kwongera ingirabuzima fatizo za epithelial, no kongera macrophages nabyo byaragaragariye mu barwayi ba SARS.
Ikindi kandi, abagera kuri 20-30% by'abarwayi bakenera kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Uretse mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, hari izindi ngingo zimwe na zimwe zirimo urwungano rw'igifu, uruhu n'impyiko na zo zishobora kwandura mu gihe byakabaye bikomeye, akenshi zikaba zifite ibyorezo by'indwara z'amahoronoke, kandi bishobora guhitana abantu, cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ubumuga.
Virusi yatangiriye mu gupima ibihaha byagenewe mwene wabo wa zero wari ugiye muri Hong Kong avuye i Guangzhou.
Kuva icyo gihe, hakozwe imbaraga nyinshi mu bushakashatsi bwa HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yabonetse mu bana b'amezi arindwi bo mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Iyi virusi yabanje kugaragara cyane mu bana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwayi bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona bafite uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Kurwara indwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63 biragaragara cyane mu ndwara ziterwa na koresa, konjiktiviti, umuriro n'imyanda yo mu mara.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje ko virusi nk'iyo yabonetse mu cyuma cy'umunwa w'umwana w'umuhungu w'amezi umunani urwaye umusonga mu Buholandi.
Nubwo byamenyekanye mu Buholandi, iyi virusi yageze ku isi yose.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 igaragaza hafi 4.7% by'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikunze kubaho kandi ko yibonekeza cyane mu itangira ry'impeshyi, itumba n'itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano na laryngite y'uruti rw'umugongo, nanone yitwa croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari urwariye mu bitaro kubera umusonga n'imyanda yo mu mara mu gihugu cya Hong Kong.
Uretse indwara z'ibihaha n'iz'ibihaha, HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ibihaha.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E, na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 iboneka ku isi hose, ituma indwara z'ubuhumekero buciriritse.
Izi HCoV z'imiryango ine zose zarahindutse abantu kandi muri rusange zifite amahirwe make yo guhinduka indwara ziteye indwara cyane.Nyamara, hari izindi nyinshi z'umwihariko zibayeho ku mpamvu zitazwi, nk'uko byagenze mu gihe cy'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63 burusha ubundi kuba bwinshi bwa vuba aha bwavuzwe ko butera indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe, iyo hagize ubushobozi bwo kwimuka neza no gukomeza kwigirira icyizere mu bantu, virusi ya HCoV na yo igabanuka.
MERS-CoV yatangiriye mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 ufite indwara y'ibihaha n'impyiko mu gihugu cya Arabiya Sawudite.
Nubwo abenshi mu barwayi bemejwe n'abashakashatsi bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari abanduye mu bihugu by'i Burayi na Tuniziya.
Indi ndwara ya kabiri yabereye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 aho abantu 186 bemejwe ko banduye.
Imyitozo ya MERS isa n'iyo muri SARS, irangwa n'indwara y'ibihaha igenda yiyongera.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi ba MERS na bo barwara indwara y'impyiko zikomeye, kugeza ubu MERS niyo yonyine ibamo indwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu maraso, nk'indwara y'umwijima no gusubiranamo.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi barenga 2500 bemejwe n'abashakashatsi, kandi umubare w'abapfa ni 34,4%, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi ziteye ubwoba cyane abantu bazi.
Hagati y'ukwezi kwa 12 kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa 12, 2019, itsinda ry'abarwayi ba pneumonia baherutse guhura n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 ryavumbuwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iri gukorwa kandi iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abantu ku isi, kandi ko cyiswe COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90,053 nibo bamaze kwandura ku isi hose, aho umubare w'abapfa ku bwandu bwa virusi itera SIDA uri kuri 3,4%.
Ni ngombwa ko tumenya ko, umubare w'abandura muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa, ari 4.2%, mu gihe umubare w'abandura hanze ya Hubei ari 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 iteza indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zigaragaramo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Indwara y'igifu na yo yasanzwe mu barwayi bake.
Pneumonia ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye kandi bishobora guhinduka vuba bikaba syndrome y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zisa cyane kubera homologie yo mu rwego rwa nucleotide iri hejuru, ku kigero cya 82%, zombi ziri mu ishami ry'igiti cy'imiterere itandukanye.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 iranduza cyane, ariko irandura cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 badafite ibimenyetso by'indwara baramaze kuvugwa kandi bashobora kuba baragize uruhare mu gukwirakwira kwa SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bwihuse ku isi hose.
Kugereranya no gutandukanya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi HCoV esheshatu byerekana ibintu byinshi bihambaye bihuriyeho n'itandukaniro.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro n'igihe indwara ya HCoV imara birasa cyane.
Muri ubwo buryo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza imiterere y'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ubukana bwa COVID-19 buri hagati ya SARS-CoV na izindi HCoV enye z'umuryango (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ishusho y'ubwandu bwa HCoVs rusange, ikubiyemo ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, umubare muto w'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu buryo bukabije ushobora gusa n'uwanduye SARS-CoV nubwo ari ku kigero cyo hasi cyane.
Icya gatatu, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 na bwo bugaragaza ibimenyetso bishishikaje, bufite aho bihuriye na HCoV y'umuryango na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwo bwanduzwa n'ubundi bufite ubushobozi bungana n'ubwa HCoV z'abaturage.
Ku rundi ruhande, kugabanya ubushobozi bwo kwanduzanya bwa SARS-CoV-2 nyuma y'inzira zimwe na zimwe mu bantu biracyakenewe kwemezwa, nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Icya nyuma, kimwe n'izindi HCoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bimera by'ibinure.
"Ese kwanduzanya SARS-CoV-2 mu myanya y'umubiri n'umunwa bifite akamaro, nk'uko bimeze ku kwanduzanya SARS-CoV, nibura mu bihe bimwe na bimwe, bigomba gusobanurwa n'ubundi bushakashatsi".
Ikindi cy'ingenzi ni ukumenya niba SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo nk'uko bimeze kuri HCoV z'abaturage.
Icyakora, isura ya SARS-CoV-2, ikubiyemo ubushobozi bwo kwanduzanya, ubwandu, no gukwirakwira mu buryo burambye mu nzira nyinshi mu bantu, izagira ingaruka zikomeye ku iherezo ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje.
HCoVs enye z'umuryango zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje zose zarahindutse abantu.
Urebye mu buryo bunyuranye, abantu bashobora kuba barahinduye imiterere y'izo HCoV uko ari enye.
Mu yandi magambo, HCoVs n'abantu bashobora kuba ari ubwoko bw'abantu barokotse icyorezo cya HCoVs cyo mu bihe bya kera.
HCoV zateye indwara zikomeye mu bantu n'abantu barwaye indwara zikomeye z'ubwoko bwa HCoV zarakemutse.
Kugira ngo ibyo bibe, HCoV igomba kwiyongera mu bantu ku buryo buhagije kugira ngo yemere kwiyongera kw'impinduka mu buryo bw'imiterere kugira ngo irwanye ibintu biyibuza kuba mu bakiriye.
Bityo, uko igihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kirushaho kwiyongera kandi abantu benshi bakarushaho kwandura, ni na ko bishoboka ko iyi virusi ishobora kwihanganira abantu.
Niba virusi ihindutse neza, kwandurira abantu bizagorana guhagarika ikurwaho cyangwa izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu.
Mu myaka myinshi, hari udukoko tubiri tugize umuryango wa CoVs dukwirakwira mu bantu, dutera ibicurane mu bantu bafite ubumuga.
Iyi virusi ntikeneye ikigega cy'inyamaswa.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ziteye indwara cyane ntizigeze zihindurira imiterere mu bantu kandi ntizishobora kwanduzwa mu bantu.
