Ivugurura ry'amabwiriza yo gusuzuma abatekerejweho  n'abemejweho  COVID-19 rikenewe
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryatangaje inama yihuse ku bijyanye no gusuzuma no guhangana n'ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV). Iyi nama ishingiye ku byatubayeho kandi ni urugero rwiza rwo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi hose.
Nubwo icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ari icyorezo gishya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite biragenda byiyongera bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo kugikemura n'uburyo bwo kugikemura bugenda buhinduka.
Muri iyi baruwa, dusubiza ku bitekerezo biri mu mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya by'ubushakashatsi ku uburwayi bwitezwe n'ubwemejwe bishingiye ku mabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Inyandiko ya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi iyo virusi yitwa coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yavuze ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye amabwiriza yihuse yo gutanga inama, maze ayo mabwiriza asohoka kuri interineti mu kinyamakuru cya Military Medical Research ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020.
Iyo mfashanyigisho imaze gushishikaza abantu benshi kuva yasohoka.
Icyakora, ni ngombwa kumenya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo kuyisuzuma no kuyirwanya bugenda buhinduka.
Urugero ni Igitabo cy'Inyigisho n'Inyigisho ku ndwara ya COVID-19 cyatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), kuva ku ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, iki kigo cyasohoye amagazeti arindwi yose hamwe n'ibitabo bimwe na bimwe byahindutse.
Ubuyobozi bwacu bwitabiriye ibitekerezo bya Zhou et al., batanze igitekerezo cyo gutanga amanota yoroheje ashingiye ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Ibyavuye mu bikorwa byabo byongereye ibihamya bishya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi biba iby'agaciro mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Dushyigikiye umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi tubasuhuza.
Icyakora, ibyo bagezeho bikeneye kuvugururwa bishingiye ku mabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no guhangana na COVID-19 (igitabo cya karindwi cy'igerageza) n'inyigo ziherutse gukorwa.
Dukurikije inyandiko ya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kwemeza umuntu ukekwaho ubwandu bisaba guhuza kimwe mu bisobanuro by'amateka y'icyorezo n'ibintu bibiri by'ubuvuzi kugira ngo habeho isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa bisaba kuzuza ibintu bitatu by'ubuvuzi mu gihe nta mateka y'icyorezo bigaragara:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (banyuze mu bipimo bya nucleic acid); (3) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abarwayi barwaye umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) amateka y'abamenyanye n'itsinda ry'abantu banduye (≥2 banduye umuriro na/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu byumweru 2 mu duce duto, nk'amazu, ibiro, ibyumba by'amashuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso by'igaragaza ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) imibare yose y'utugingo tw'amaraso yera igaragaza ko umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso ari usanzwe, wagabanutse cyangwa wagabanutse mu ntangiriro.
Gushakisha umuntu wemejwe ko yanduye bigomba gushingira ku muntu ukekwaho uburwayi afite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu cyangwa se ibimenyetso bya seriyoloji bikurikira: (1) ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya PCR cyakoze ubushakashatsi ku gihe cya SARS-CoV-2; (2) urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima byose bya virusi bigaragaza ko ari kimwe ku virusi nshya izwi; (3) ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyakoze ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa IgM n'ubundi bwoko bwa IgG mu gusuzuma SARS-CoV-2 mu maraso; cyangwa se ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyakoze ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa IgG mu gihe cya SARS-CoV-2 cyakoze ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 kigahinduka kigahinduka kigahinduka kigafasha, cyangwa se titre y'uburwayi yiyongeraho inshuro ≥4 mu gihe cyo gukira hejuru y'ibipimo byo mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo bya aside ya nucleate mu bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso byongewemo mu cyiciro cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Kumenya indwara mu maraso byongerewe mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu cya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma, ibimenyetso bya serolojiya byongerewe mu cyiciro cya karindwi.
Iri hinduka rishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi mu gushakisha ibikoresho byiza byo gupima aside ya nucleic ku buryo bwo gupima vuba, ndetse n'ibipimo by'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero birimo gufata amaraso, byongera iboneka ry'ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi bigashyigikira kwinjiza umusaruro mwiza w'umubiri runaka mu bipimo byemejwe.
Ikindi kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bitwibutsa ko tugomba kwitondera abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje n'abadafite ibimenyetso.
Ku bw'ibyo, imibare y'ibanze ya Zhou et al. yagombaga kuvugururwa kuko bagena abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi nk'abafite ibyago bike.
Uburyo bwo gutanga amanota nabwo bukeneye kwemezwa mu bikorwa no mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko ibimenyetso by'imvaho bizagaragara kandi tugasaba abasomyi bacu kugira icyo batangaza.
Ku barwayi bagaragaweho indwara z'ubwandu n'iz'ubwandu, turabasaba gukurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'igihugu.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera kandi kuvugurura amabwiriza yacu buri gihe kugirango dufashe.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini w'abapfa ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe bazize iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye w'ubwandu bwa virusi itera SIDA ugizwe n'abantu 114 bari mu bikorwa byo kurwanya indwara n'abandi 33 bakize bari mu ngo zabo.
Abantu 17 ni bo bamaze gupfa.
Mu kiganiro cy'amakuru cyanyujijwe kuri interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye barimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Nk'uko Dr Meerjady abivuga, babiri bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60, n'undi umwe wari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu bapfuye bakomokaga i Dhaka.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikigo cy'amakuru cyo muri ako gace, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo ya Bengali yo kurwanya ruswa, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa Gatandatu, mu itangazo ryashyizwe kuri videwo, Minisitiri w'Ubutwererane n'Amashanyarazi, Obaidul Quader yavuze ko imodoka zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe, kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Ibi byahagarikwa by'ingendo rusange byatangiye ku ya 26 Werurwe kandi biteganyijwe ko bizarangira ku wa Gatandatu, tariki ya 4 Mata.
Gucuruza ibintu by'ibanze - imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa - biracyemewe.
Icyorezo cya mbere cya COVID-19 cyagaragaye muri Bangladesh ku ya 8 Werurwe, ku bantu babiri bari bavuye mu Butaliyani n'umugore wa umwe muri bo.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, abo bantu uko ari batatu bari bakize.
Ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwarenze miliyoni ku isi hose
Ku wa Kane, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 warenze miliyoni ku isi, nk'uko byatangajwe na Johns Hopkins University.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52 bapfuye bazize COVID-19, indwara iterwa na koronavirusi.
Ibi byagarutse ku munsi umwe Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus na Zambia yabonye urupfu rwa mbere rw'umuntu ufitanye isano na coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ku wa Kane ko ari kimwe mu bihugu bike byasigaye bitanduye coronavirus.
Kugeza ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje ko abantu 1,051,635 banduye, barimo 79,332 mu masaha 24 ashize kuva saa kumi za mu gitondo ku isaha yo mu Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (USA), hamaze kugaragara abarwayi barenga ibihumbi 244 ba coronavirus, iki cyorezo kikaba cyaratumye hapfa abantu bagera kuri 5900.
Ikigo cy'amakuru cya CBS cyatangaje ko hakurikijwe amakuru ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, muri Amerika hapfuye abantu barenga 1000 bishwe n'ubwandu bwa coronavirus.
Hirya no hino ku isi, ibihugu byatangaje ko byashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Ku wa Kane, Sergei Sobyanin, umuyobozi w'umujyi wa Moscou, yongeye igihe cyo guhagarika abantu mu karere kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko abaturage b'Uburusiya bazakomeza guhembwa nta kazi basabwa gukora kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Portugal yatangaga amajwi yo kongera igihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe mu gihugu mu gihe cy'iminsi 15; ayo majwi yatanzwe n'amajwi 215 yo gushyigikira, icumi yo kwima, n'ijambo rimwe ryo kwanga.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha y'ijoro mu mijyi yera ya Mecca na Medina kugeza umunsi wose; mbere, amasaha y'ijoro yari hagati ya saa tatu z'amanywa na saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo gusa.
Thailand irateganya gushyiraho amasaha y'ijoro hagati ya saa kumi z'ijoro na saa yine za mu gitondo.
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye amasaha yo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yagabanyije umubare w'utubati two mu bwiherero
Ku Cyumweru no ku wa Gatandatu nyuma ya saa sita, amaduka yo muri Australia Woolworth na Coles yagabanyije imipaka yo kugura udupfunyika two mu bwiherero, ku bicuruzwa bibiri na paketi imwe mu maduka yose yo mu gihugu.
ALDI kandi yashyizeho imipaka y'ipaki imwe, ku wa mbere.
Ibi bihano byatangajwe nk'ubutumwa ku biro by'itora no ku rubuga rwa Facebook rw'urubuga rwe.
Abaguzi bavuga ko bari mu bikorwa byo kwizigamira kubera gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe abaturage bari kuba bagomba kwicumbikira.
Ku wa Gatatu, Woolworths nayo yagabanyije ibiciro byo kugura utubati two mu bwiherero ku byo kuzana ku nzu kugeza ku isanduku imwe ku busabe.
Iri hinduka rikurikira ibihano by'amapafari ane ku bucuruzi bwa mbere byashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Mu itangazo ry'itangazamakuru ryo ku ya 8 Werurwe, Coles yatangaje ko mu gihe hashyizweho ibihano byo gutwara ibicuruzwa mu byiciro bine, "amaduka menshi akomeje kubura ibicuruzwa mu gihe cy'isaha imwe kuva byoherejwe", avuga ko ibyo bisabwa "bitigeze bibaho mbere", mu gihe ALDI, mu butumwa yashyize kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri, yabyise "bitunguranye".
Umuvugizi wa Woolworths yavuze ko mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa "byarazamutse cyane".
Amaduka ya Costco yo muri Canberra na yo yagabanyije umubare w'ibikoresho yemerewe mu bipaketi bibiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo wirinde kubura, Coles yategetse ibicuruzwa byinshi cyane ku batanga ibicuruzwa kandi yongera umubare w'ibikoresho, Woolworths yategetse ibicuruzwa byinyongera, mu gihe ALDI yatumye ibicuruzwa byo ku wa gatatu udasanzwe byamamaza biboneka hakiri kare.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko ya leta y'aho batuye ku gihe cyo kohereza amakamyo atuma bigorana.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, mu gihe abaguzi bazaba bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi hazabaho amatangazo make.
Ku wa Kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko kubera ko yari imaze gusohora ibicuruzwa hakiri kare, amaduka amwe n'amwe atashoboraga gukora ibirori byo ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru yatanzwe na News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi muri kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibikoresho buri mugoroba.
Yashimangiye ko utubati ari ibintu bifite ubunini bwinshi ku buryo umubare wabyo uba muto, kandi ko iyo tuguze, twongera imyanya myinshi ku mashami, bityo ibyo bintu bikagenda bigabanuka.
Coles na Woolworths bavuga [ko] niba hari ibintu byinshi ku kibaho, niba ibicuruzwa nk'isuku y'isuku n'ibikoresho byo kwisiga bishobora [gucuruzwa] kandi bikaba bihari ku bwinshi, ubwoba bushobora kugabanuka, nk'uko Russel Zimmerman abivuga binyuze kuri ABC News.
Uwakoze utwo dukingirizo twa 'Who Gives a Crap' yavuze ko ku wa gatatu ushize nta bikoresho bari bafite.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora ibikoresho byo gusukura mu bwiherero bya Kleenex, na Solaris Paper, ikora Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bakora amasaha 24 n'amasaha 7 kugira ngo bakomeze kubikoresha, nk'uko amakuru atangwa na News.com.au abivuga.
Urubuga rw'imicungire y'imitungo, Domain.com, rwatangaje ko abagurisha amazu bamwe batanze udupfunyika tw'isuku ku buntu ku ba mbere batanze ibiciro mu cyamunara i Melbourne, mu gihe hari ibiciro bike by'ibinyabiziga byatanzwe kubera ko abaguzi bafataga ikiruhuko cy'impera z'icyumweru.
Umunara w'Umurinzi wo ku wa Kane w'ikinyamakuru cyitwa NT News, cyandikirwa i Darwin, wari urimo amapaji umunani y'ibikoresho byari bigenewe gukata no gukoreshwa nk'udupfunyika two mu bwiherero.
Mu by'ukuri, amaduka yanze gushyiraho ibihano, nk'uko ABC Australia yabitangaje ku ya 3 Werurwe, ivuga ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho ibihano byo kugura.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bikoresho na byo bikenewe cyane, harimo udupfukamunwa, imyenda, ibyokurya bikonjesha, isabune yo koza intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku Cyumweru nimugoroba, isoko rikora ku rubuga rwa interineti ryo mu Bwongereza ryitwa Ocado ryabonye ko kugura utubati two mu bwiherero twa Andres bigabanyaga ku bipimo bibiri by'udupfunyika 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku buryo indwara yageze kure, aho kwerekeza ku buryo iki cyorezo gishobora guteza akaga, OMS ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza leta kugira icyo ikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura inzira y'iki cyorezo.
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko niba ibihugu byamenye, bikagerageza, bikita ku bantu, bikabashyira mu kato kandi bikabakusanya mu rwego rwo kubisubiza.
Dufite impungenge nyinshi kubera uko gukwirakwira n'uburemere byateje impungenge, ariko nanone kubera ko ibikorwa byatewe n'ihindagurika biteye impungenge.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara abivuga, icyo cyorezo "nticyigeze kibaho mbere hose".
Mu nyandiko CNN yashyize ahagaragara mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, yavuze ko "uretse ibicurane, nta zindi virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigeze zigaragara kuva zavutse kugeza ubwo zikwirakwijwe ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus yavuze ko na we ari uko abibona, agira ati "ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara nshya ya pandemic ikurikiye icyemezo cy'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) mu kwezi kwa mbere cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'indwara y'uburwayi bw'abaturage gihangayikishije isi yose.
Dr. Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara Zandura n'Izandura, yavuze ko icyo cyorezo "kizarushaho kwiyongera".
Kugeza ku wa Kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko hari nibura abantu 126.000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi hose, bihitana abantu barenga 4.600.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ikomeje kandi iterwa na coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, mu Kuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'Icyorezo cy'Ubuzima bw'Igihugu ku Isi ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020, ndetse gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bahitanwa n'abantu bagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bamaze gukira.
Umubare w'abandura ugereranywa na 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe ku isi hose ugera kuri 13.04% kugeza kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle Zelande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe ni umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora kuba bikubiyemo umusonga n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Igihe kuva ku isohorwa kugeza ku kugaragaza ibimenyetso muri rusange ni iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza kuri cumi n'ine.
Nta rukingo rw'umwihariko rw'indwara ya virusi cyangwa imiti izwi.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvurwa ni uburyo bwo kuvura ibimenyetso n'ubufasha. Ingamba zo kwirinda zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa igihe ukoroye, kugendera kure abandi, no kugenzura no kwicungira mu kato abantu bakekwaho kwandura.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibi bikorwa bashyiraho amategeko yo kugabanya ingendo, guhagarika abantu, amasaha yo gutaha, kugenzura akaga ku kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye mu bukungu n'imibereho y'abantu ku isi, gusezera cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa by'umuco, politiki, amadini, siporo, n'ubukene bw'ibicuruzwa bwongereweho kugura ibintu mu buryo butunguranye.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu no ku rwego rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99,4 ku ijana by'abanyeshuri ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri iyi virusi yakwirakwiriye kuri interineti kandi hari ibikorwa by'ivangura n'ivangura ku bantu bo mu Bushinwa, abantu bafite inkomoko n'imiterere byo mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Uburasirazuba bwa Aziya, n'abantu bakomoka mu duce dufite ubwandu bwinshi.
Kubera kugabanya ingendo no gufunga inganda zikomeye, guhumanya ikirere no kohereza umwuka wa karubone byagabanutse.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei), bwavuze ko hari amaterasi y'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kandi ko iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Ibi byaha byiganjemo ibijyanye n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, bityo bikekwa ko virusi ifite inkomoko yo mu bwoko bw'ibikoko.
Virusi yateje icyorezo yitwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi ivumbuwe vuba kandi ifitanye isano na coronavirus y'ikivumbi, coronavirus y'ikinyugunyugu na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wagaragayeho ibimenyetso nyuma yaje kurwara ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano bigaragara afitanye na cya gisata cy'amasoko y'amazi cyavuzwe nyuma.
Mu matsinda y'abanduye ba mbere batangajwe mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse bifitanye isano n'uru ruganda.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itari yemejwe ya South China Morning Post yatangaje ko ubwandu bushobora gutangira ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, ku mugabo w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, bishoboka ko ari ubwa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko, hamwe n'ubwandu bushya bwatangajwe bwagabanutse mu Bushinwa, ariko bukaba bwarakabije mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere.
Hashobora kuba hari umubare munini w'abantu batavugwaho ibimenyetso, cyane cyane mu bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, umubare muto w'abanduye wari umaze kumenyekana mu rubyiruko, aho abantu bafite imyaka 19 n'abari munsi yayo bagize 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru mu bya siyansi w'Ubwongereza, Patrick Vallance, ateganya ko 60% by'abatuye Ubwongereza bakeneye kwandura mbere yuko ubwirinzi bw'itsinda bushobora kugerwaho.
Umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga baranduye COVID-19 kandi ibipimo byabo byemejwe ko ari byiza nk'uko amategeko abiteganya.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho politiki zemewe yo kudapima abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 batari barigeze bamenyekana, kandi ko ubwo bwandu butanditse ari bwo bwatumye haboneka 79% by'ubwandu bwanditse.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mibare bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 30 Werurwe, bugaragaza ko umubare w'abandura mu Butaliyani ushobora kuba munini cyane kuruta umubare w'abanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abana bavukana (R0) wa COVID-19 uri hagati ya 1.4 na 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, bwagaragaje ko uwo mubare ushobora kuba uri munsi ya 5.7.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 barakize.
Ku bantu batakize, igihe kuva ibimenyetso bitangira kugeza ku rupfu kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, kandi akenshi ni iminsi 14.
Kuva ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 bamaze gupfa bazize COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'impfu z'abantu bapfuye bari bafite imyaka 60 kuzamura na 75% bari bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima byari bisanzwe biriho, birimo indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Imibare y'urupfu rwemewe na leta kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange yerekeza ku bantu bapfuye bapimwe bagasanga barwaye COVID hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Imibare y'abapfuye by'ukuri kubera COVID-19 ishobora kuba iri hejuru cyane, kubera ko imibare yemewe ishobora kuba itarimo abapfuye batapimwe, urugero nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi n'ibindi.
Amakuru amwe n'amwe y'u Butaliyani yagaragaje ko umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo warenze umubare w'abapfuye bishwe na COVID ku buryo bukubye inshuro 4-5.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] uri hasi cyane ugereranyije n'umubare nyawo", amagambo yakomejwe n'amakuru atazwi neza ku byerekeye imibare iri hasi cyane muri Amerika. Imibare iri hasi cyane ikunze kugaragara mu ndwara z'ibyorezo, nk'uko byagenze mu cyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube H1N1 mu 2009.
Impamvu ya mbere y'urupfu hanze y'Ubushinwa ni uko rwabaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho iyambere y'urupfu hanze ya Aziya ikaba mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abantu barenga icumi na babiri barapfuye muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu birenga mirongo ine n'uturere byatangaje ko abantu bapfuye, ku migabane yose, uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi biganishwa n'umubare w'ibizamini, ubwiza bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kugenzura, igihe kuva icyorezo cya mbere cyatangira, n'imiterere y'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina, n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ibarura rya Johns Hopkins University, umubare w'abishwe n'ubwandu ku isi ni 6.0% (97.039/1.617.204) ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Iyo mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'urupfu ku barwayi yagabanutse iva kuri 17.3% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso nyuma ya 1 Gashyantare 2020).Izindi ngero zirimo umubare w'abandura (CFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bagaragaweho indwara bapfa bazize indwara runaka, n'umubare w'abanduye indwara bapfa bazize indwara (IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abanduye (bafite indwara kandi batayigaragaweho) bapfa bazize indwara runaka.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ifitanye isano n'igihe kandi ikurikira abaturage kuva ku banduye kugeza ku barwayi.
Hari intiti zagiye zigerageza kubara iyo mibare ku baturage runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso gitanga imibare y'urupfu rw'ubwandu bw'icyorezo muri rusange hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibipimo byo hejuru by'ibipimo by'ibura bihuje n'ibyavuye mu igerageza rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu Budage n'ubushakashatsi bw'ibarurishamibare bwasuzumye ingaruka z'ibipimo ku ngengabihe ya CFR.
OMS yemeje ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'ikirenga n'igihe cy'iherezo by'icyo cyorezo ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'ahantu.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya leta ya Pennsylvania yagize ati "nubwo indwara zandura zidakomeje, akenshi ziba zisanzwe kandi zigatangira kugabanuka iyo zibuze umukumbi.
Ariko kandi, muri iki gihe, gukora imibare ishyize mu gaciro y'igihe ibyo bizabera, biragoye cyane".
Umujyanama wa leta y'Ubushinwa mu by'ubuvuzi, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "iki cyorezo gishobora kurangira muri Kamena" mu gihe ibihugu byose byashishikarizwa gukurikiza inama za OMS ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere ry'i Londres yavuze ko SRS-CoV-2 "izakomeza gukwirakwira, bishoboka ko mu gihe cy'umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
Nk'uko bivugwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson wo muri Imperial College, kugabanya ingendo n'ibindi bikorwa bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (hashobora gushira amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bishoboka ko iyi koronavirusi, kubera ko yandura cyane, ishobora kuzimira burundu" kandi ko iyi ndwara "ishobora guhinduka indwara y'igihe, igaruka buri mwaka".
Kuba virusi ishobora kongera kugaruka biterwa n'ubushobozi bw'itsinda ry'abanduye n'urwego rw'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'iyo virusi.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi umuntu wayanduye ashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ibanze ni umuriro (88%) n'umuhogo utoshye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara cyane ni umunaniro, guhumeka amazuru (flagmata), kubura ubushobozi bwo guhumeka, guhumeka nabi, ububabare mu ngingo n'ingingo, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, kugira ubwoba, gusubiranamo, kugira amaraso, iseseme, cyangwa cyanoze.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso by'impanuka birimo guhumeka nabi, mu gatuza hafunze cyangwa mu gatuza haheze, gucikamo ibice, kugendana nabi, no kugira ubururu ku maso no ku munwa; kwihutira kwitabwaho n'abaganga birasabwa iyo ibi bimenyetso bibonetse.
Abantu bamwe na bamwe banduye bashobora kuba bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagaragaza ko abantu bahuye cyane n'abantu banduye bagomba gukurikiranwa cyane no gusuzumwa kugira ngo barebe ko batanduye.
Abashinwa bavuga ko umubare w'abandura uturuka ku bindi byorezo ugera kuri 44%.
Igihe cyo kubamo (igihe kiri hagati yo kwandura no kugaragaza ibimenyetso) akenshi kiri hagati y'iminsi 1 na 14, akenshi ni iminsi 5. Urugero rw'ibihe bidashidikanywaho, imibare y'abantu barwaye COVID-19 batakaza impumuro mu ntangiriro ni 30%, hanyuma igabanuka ikajya kuri 15%.
Ibisobanuro birambuye ku buryo iyo ndwara ikwirakwira biracyakorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Kwandura COVID-19 byitezwe ko byibasira cyane cyane mu gihe cyo guhura no mu gihe cy'ibitonyanga by'amaraso biboneka mu gihe cyo gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga; guhura ni guhura hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (3 na 6 z'ibirenge).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukorora udafite icyo utwikiriye bishobora gutuma amazi atemba muri metero 15 kugeza kuri metero 8.2.
Abashakashatsi bamwe batekereza ko virusi ishobora no gutangwa n'udutonyanga duto tumara igihe kirekire mu kirere kandi dukomoka mu gihe umuntu avuga. Utunyoni two mu myanya y'ubuhumekero dushobora no gutangwa mu gihe umuntu ahumetse, harimo no mu gihe avuga, nubwo iyi virusi idakunze kwanduzwa mu kirere.
Utwo duce dushobora kugwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi yacu cyangwa tukava mu mwuka tugana mu bihaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura, urugero nko gutera mu mwuka w'amaraso (intubatsion) no guhagarika imitsi y'amaraso (RCP), bushobora gutuma umwuka uhinduka umuti wo guhumeka, hanyuma ukajya mu kirere.
Nanone kandi, umuntu ashobora kuyandura iyo akoze ku kintu cyanduye, harimo uruhu, amaso, izuru n'umunwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko virusi ishobora gukwirakwira mu busa, iki kibazo cyitezwe ko kiri hasi.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduzwa mu myanya y'umubiri. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo ikwirakwira rishobora kuba mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara no mu gihe cy'uburwayi.
Abantu bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara mbere y'iminsi itatu, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ushobora kuyandura mbere y'uko ugira ibimenyetso bikomeye.
Hari raporo nke z'abanduye asymptomatic zemejwe muri laboratwari, ariko ubwandu bwa asymptomatic bwamaze kumenyekana n'ibihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gihe cyo gukora iperereza ku bantu bahuye.
