Coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, ya mbere yatandukanyijwe n'abantu batatu barwaye ibicurane by'imyotsi ifitanye isano n'ihuriro ry'abarwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero i Wuhan.
Imiterere yose ya virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na coronavirus mu bidukikije. Hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi ishobora gusenywa iyo ihuye n'isabune yo mu rugo, ikangiza igifu cyayo cy'ubwirinzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV ya mbere.
Bivugwa ko iyi virusi ikomoka ku nyamaswa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo ryagaragaje ko koronavirusi ihuje n'ubwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, mu bwoko bwa Sarbecovirus (umurongo wa B) hamwe n'udutsiko tubiri tw'ingore.
Iyi virusi ifite umwihariko wa 96% ku rwego rwa genom yose hamwe n'ibindi bipimo bya koronavirusi y'ikinyugunyugu (BatCov RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi b'Abashinwa bavumbuye ko hari itandukaniro ry'amino asidi imwe gusa mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya genomic sequence hagati ya virusi ya shingles na virusi y'umuntu.
Kugeza ubu, kugereranya ibinyabuzima byose by'umuntu umwe byerekana ko 92% by'ibinyabuzima bya koronavirusi ya tungurusumu na SARS-CoV-2 bihuje, ariko ntibihagije kugira ngo byemezwe ko tungurusumu ari yo nyirabayazana wa SARS-CoV-2.
