CDC itera inkunga ko mu gihe hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko yanduye COVID mu bigo rusange, nk'ibiro cyangwa ubwiherero, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki abantu bakoresha nk'utubanda, utwuma dukoresha utwuma duto, ibyuma bya elegitoroniki, ibyuma by'ibinyabiziga, ibyuma bya kure, na ATM bikoreshwa n'abarwayi, bigomba kwandura.
