Ivangura ry'imibanire (ryitwa kandi iry'umubiri) ni igikorwa cyo kurwanya indwara kigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Uburyo bwo gukumira abantu mu mibereho y'abaturage burimo guhagarika abantu; gukumira ingendo; no gufunga amashuri, ibigo by'akazi, za sitade, za sinema cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gushyiraho uburyo bwo kwirinda mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha indamukanyo zitagaragara no kugirana n'abandi imishyikirano ya bugufi.
Muri iki gihe, leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa zisaba ko abantu bareka kujya mu gace kagwiririwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare w'abantu benshi bagombaga guhurira hamwe ugereranyije n'abandi bantu benshi, nk'uko byasabwaga n'inzego za Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima, wagabanutse cyane, uva ku bantu 250 (niba nta COVID-19 izwi mu karere) ugera ku bantu 50, hanyuma ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza guteranira ahantu hahurira abantu benshi. Abasaza n'abantu bafite ibibazo by'uburwayi nk'indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso, n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'ibibazo by'indwara, CDC yasabye ko mu gihe bishoboka baba mu ngo zabo gusa mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo ku rwego rw'abaturage. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye guhindura ikoreshwa ry'ijambo "guhagarika imishyikirano" ku "guhagarika imishyikirano", kugira ngo bisobanuke ko intego ari ukugabanya guhura mu buryo bwagutse binyuze mu gukomeza imishyikirano, haba mu buryo bwa virtual cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "ibihano by'imibereho" byumvikanisha ko abantu bagomba kwigunga byuzuye mu mibanire yabo kandi ntibashishikarize abantu gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi binyuze mu bundi buryo.
Muri izo nama harimo no gusaba ko wakora imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana nawe gusa kandi udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Kwishyira ukwabo mu rugo byasabwe ku bantu bagaragaweho COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuyandura.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwigunga neza. Leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa zigatanga inama yo kwigunga ku baturage bose baba mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura ku giti cye atangwa ku bantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragaragaweho COVID-19 n'abantu baherutse gukora ingendo mu bihugu cyangwa uturere dufite ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 barasabwa kwiherera mu kato k'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashoboraga kuheruka kugaragazwamo.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa kucyirwanya, no kucyirinda.
Gufunga bikorwa mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gutandukanya abantu banduye no gufata izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira zigamije guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu baturage bose.
Iyo bitagishoboka guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara, imbaraga zikurikiyeho zihinduka mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ibi bikorwa bikorwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Ihuriro ry'ibikorwa byo gukumira no kugabanya bishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Ihohoterwa rikeneye ingamba z'icyorezo mu buryo bukabije mu kugabanya umubare w'abana bavuka munsi ya 1. Igice cyo gucunga icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ugushaka kugabanya icyorezo, kizwiho gutera ibipimo by'icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kurengerwa n'ubuvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibiganiro by'ubuvuzi bidashingiye ku miti byo guhangana n'icyorezo birimo ingamba z'ubwirinzi ku bantu, nk'isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa, no kwisanzura; ingamba ku rwego rw'abaturage zigamije kugabanya imikorere y'umubiri, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa by'iteraniro; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibi bikorwa; ndetse n'ingamba ku rwego rw'ibidukikije, nko gusukura.
Ibihugu bindi na byo byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bwo kugenzura no gushyira abantu mu kato, ndetse itanga n'inkunga ku bimuka by'abanduye.
Singapore itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye biyicarira bonyine kandi igafatira amande menshi abananirwa kubikora.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi ihana abateranya ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Imyitozo yo mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yerekana ko kugabanya (kugabanya, ariko ntibuze ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugihagarika (guhindura uburumbuke bw'icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ubwandu ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abasaba ubuvuzi mu bice bibiri bya gatatu, n'urupfu mu gice cya kabiri, ariko ikongera guhitana abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana n'amajana, kandi ikongeraho n'uburwayi.
Gukumira birashoboka, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikiri mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwa mbere rubonetse), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ubwandu buzazamuka vuba igihe ingamba zo kuzimya zizagabanuka.
Ibiganiro by'igihe kirekire byo guhashya icyorezo bigira ingaruka ku mibereho y'abaturage no ku bukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wemewe kuri COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuwushyira mu bikorwa, birimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti ya virusi ya grippe, kunywa amazi ahagije no kuruhuka bihagije bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo, imiti ya ogisijeni, imiti yo mu mitsi n'imiti yo guhumeka bishobora gukenerwa.
Gukoresha steroid bishobora gutuma umurwayi arushaho kuremba.
Hari imiti imwe n'imwe yari yemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwa virusi iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi ivuga ko hari "imiti gakondo n'imiti yo mu rugo" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza serivisi z'ubuzima n'ibyo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ari intambwe y'ibanze mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere bya WHO ku mugabane w'u Burayi byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'inzego z'ubuzima bw'ibanze yo kwimura ibikoresho ku rwego rutandukanye, harimo no gushyira imbaraga mu ikoranabuhanga mu gupima COVID-19, niba bishoboka, gusesa uburyo bwo gupima, gushyira mu kato no gushyira mu kato abarwayi barwaye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bababaye cyane binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'abatanga umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku nkomoko y'uburwayi bwa mbere (bwitwa uburwayi bwa zero).
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho icyorezo cya coronavirus yavumbuwe tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi bibazo ahanini bifitanye isano n'Isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, rikunda kugurisha inyamaswa nzima, kandi igitekerezo kimwe kivuga ko virusi yavuye muri kimwe muri ibi bikoko; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, virusi ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan babwiye bagenzi babo ko hari "indwara ya coronavirus isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani muri abo, barimo Li Wenliang, baragabishijwe n'abapolisi kubera ko bakwirakwizaga ibihuha by'ibinyoma, naho undi, Ai Fen, yacyashwe n'abakozi bakuru be kubera ko yatanze umuburo.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan yahise itanga itangazo ku mugaragaro ku ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha OMS.
Umubare munini w'abantu bataramenyekana barwaye indwara y'ibicurane by'ibihaha byatangajwe n'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ibyo bikaba byaratumye hatangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze no mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, ishyigikiwe n'impunzi zo mu gihe cy'Ubunani kandi kubera ko Wuhan ari ihuriro rikomeye ry'ingendo n'imihanda ya gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko bwabonye abarwayi bashya bagera ku 140 ku munsi, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe y'ubutegetsi nyuma y'aho yerekana ko abantu 6,174 bari bafite ibimenyetso ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatsinze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abanduye ku isi.Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kuvugwa ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye kandi abarenga 364,000 barakize.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere bifite nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu Karere ka Schengen bigabanya urujya n'uruza kandi bigashyiraho imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu kirimo ingamba zo kugabanya, nk'igenzurwa ry'aho umuntu ari (zwi ku izina rya Guma mu rugo, itegeko ryo kwihisha mu nzu, cyangwa irindiro ry'akarere) n'isaha yo gutaha. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abatuye isi, bari mu bwoko bw'igenzurwa ry'akarere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu irindiro ry'akarere muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu irindiro ry'akarere muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1,3 bari mu irindiro ry'akarere mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu cyiciro cy'igenzurwa ry'akarere, byazamutse bigera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 ashobora kuba yarabayeho tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itaremezwa igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari uwa 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yarebye itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibicurane bitamenyekanye ku ya 26 Ukuboza; ibitaro bye byamenyesheje CDC ya Jianghan ibigaragara kuri 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere bya jenoside by'urugero rw'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko coronavirus isa na SARS iriho.
Itangazo rigenewe abantu bose ryashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Ubwo iyi nkuru yatangazwaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo n'abapolisi kubera "gukwirakwiza ibihuha" by'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa mu ntangiriro yavuze ko nta "gihamya simusiga" y'ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukabije bwaje gusobanurwa n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu gihe cy'igikorwa cyo guhagarika abantu cyiswe "igikorwa gikomeye cyane mu mateka y'abantu", cordon sanitaire cyangwa amategeko agenga isuku yatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama kugira ngo ahagarike ingendo zijya n'izisohoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi yaguwe mu mijyi 15 yose ya Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zirabujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya wa Lunar (Umunsi wa 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko hari kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Ibitaro by'i Leishenshan byubatswe nyuma, kugira ngo bifashe abarwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ikigo cy'amakoraniro na stade, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bakerarugendo no kongera ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi.
Kaminuza zose n'amashuri mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Intara ya Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba zimwe na zimwe, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'amashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukorera kure zashyizwe mu bikorwa mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Bushinwa.
Ingendo zihagaritswe mu gihugu no hanze ya Hubei.
Imodoka zitwara abantu n'ibintu zahinduwe, kandi inzu ndangamurage zo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa zarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Gucunga urujya n'uruza rw'abantu mu mujyi ni ibintu byogeye mu mijyi myinshi, kandi abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) biteganyijwe ko bazaba bari hanze. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cyinjiriye mu cyiciro cy'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda "kwinjiza" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda yo guhagarika abantu mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 ku ba mukerarugendo bose mpuzamahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, umuntu umwe rukumbi wo mu Bushinwa bw'ubutaka bw'u Bushinwa yanduye mu gihugu mu minsi itanu mbere yaho, muri iki gihe binyuze ku mukerarugendo wari waturutse i Guangzhou avuye i Istanbul.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu mu by'ukuri ryahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Ingamba zo gukora ingendo ku munsi umwe zarakururiwe muri Hubei, uretse muri Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri akarere katangiye gufungwa. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga ya Repubulika y'Abanyamerika yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite visa cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe no ku yindi tariki, nta bisobanuro bidasanzwe by'igihe iyi politiki izarangirira.
Umuntu ushaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa agomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, leta y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije inganda n'inganda gufungura no gutanga inguzanyo ku masosiyete. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwibuka itangira umunota wa gatatu w'agahenge ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri z'ijoro, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo leta nkuru yasabye imiryango guha icyubahiro ku rubuga rwa interineti yitaye ku ngamba zo kwirinda icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habayeho kwiyongera gukomeye kw'abanduye, ahanini biturutse ku nama y'umutwe mushya w'idini i Daegu, uzwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu baturutse i Wuhan ni bo bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iryo torero, 1,261 cyangwa 13% bari baratangaje ibimenyetso.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2,000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, biyongera bagera ku 3,150 ku ya 29 Gashyantare.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basanze basanzwemo virusi.
Amategeko y'indege na yo yagize ingaruka kandi arahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ifatwa nk'iy'ingenzi kandi yateguwe neza ku isi yo gukosora virusi mu baturage, gushyira mu kato umuntu wese wanduye, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura bwagaragaje ko hari inshingano yo gutanga ibimenyetso ku giti cyabo n'abantu bavuye mu mahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu ya telefoni zigendanwa, gupima virusi ku buryo bukora ku manywa cyangwa mu modoka, ku buryo ibisubizo biboneka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu barenga 20,000 ku munsi.
Muri icyo gihe, abantu bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko isaba ko Perezida Moon akurwa ku butegetsi kubera ibyo bavuga ko leta yakoze nabi mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa se mu buryo bunyuranye, bashimira Perezida ku buryo yabyifashemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ibihugu 121 byo kuyisaba ubufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom kandi, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi yabitangaje, abantu babiri barapfuye uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere leta yatangaje zirimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twatewe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo imodoka nyinshi z'imijyi zigiye gukomeza mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya wa Peresi.
Isengero rya Shia i Qom ryagumye ryuguruye ku bayoboke b'idini rya Islam kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwira rya virusi muri Gashyantare.
Mu gihe hari abivuga ko iki cyorezo muri Irani cyatwitswe, ibihugu birenga icumi byasubije abanduye muri Irani ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abanduye 388 batangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yarahagaritswe, 23 mu bayigize 290 bagaragaweho virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura nta mananiza abavugizi b'uburenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, kandi, by'agateganyo, bakarekura imfungwa zose zikwiriye.
Byagaragajwe ko hari ibyago byinshi byo kwandura mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo by'ifungwa, nabyo bidafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, uwo ukaba ari wo mubare munini mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 cyangwa abayobozi ba leta ya Irani bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota icumi bitewe na coronavirus.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuyobozi wa OMS, bishoboka ko hari abantu benshi muri Irani barwaye kurusha abavugwa.
Byanatangajwe kandi ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'icyo gihugu mu bijyanye n'imari mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku Burenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ubwo abakerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga bagasanga barwaye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibibazo byatangiye kwiyongera cyane bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'izituruka mu Bushinwa ndetse igatangaza ibihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma yaho, icyiciro cy'abantu batagaragaye bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19, cyatangiye n'abantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo gukumira icyorezo, rikubiyemo gukumira abantu barenga 50,000 mu mijyi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
