Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika ku kigo cy'isi cyita ku buzima (OMS) kugira ngo kifashe mu bushakashatsi ku rukingo no mu bikorwa byo kurwitaho, no kurinda "abantu bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
