OMS yashimye imbaraga leta y'Ubushinwa yashyizeho mu gucunga no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yasanze hari itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004 ubwo abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga guhisha bityo bagahagarika ibikorwa byo kwirinda no gukumira iki cyorezo n'ikibazo kiriho ubu aho guverinoma nkuru "itanga ibishya buri gihe kugirango birinde ubwoba mbere y'ibiruhuko by'umwaka mushya wa Lunar".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu rwego rwo kwamagana icyemezo cya leta ya leta yo gushyiraho itegeko ryo kubuza ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea, uhagarariye OMS yavuze ko nubwo icyo cyemezo "cyumvikana ko atari icyemezo cya OMS", ariko ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cyo kwiyemeza guhashya icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane" kandi ko "kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari Icyorezo cya Gatandatu cy'Ubuzima rusange ku Isi (PHEIC), ni ukuvuga PHEIC ya gatandatu kuva icyo cyemezo cyatangira gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC yashyizwe ahagaragara kubera ko "ihangayikishijwe n'uko ishobora gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abicisha bugufi, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ku itegurwa ry'ibihano byo gutembera, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idatanga inama yo guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari azakoreshwa mu gushyigikira imyiteguro mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko byihutirwa gufasha ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye virusi mu gihe icyorezo cyadutse".
Byongeye kandi, Tedros yavuze ko "aho imbaraga zacu zigarukira ari mu gice cy'uruziga gikennye cyane" maze asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kwishora mu bikorwa uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma".Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara ya virusi.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "igisubizo cy'uko hashyizweho imbaraga zose z'umuryango w'abibumbye".
Nyuma, Umuryango w'Abibumbye watangije Itsinda ry'Ubuyobozi bw'Ibiza kugira ngo rishobore guhuza ibisubizo byose bya ONU, nk'uko WHO ibivuga, bizatuma "bibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo mu rwego rw'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere rirenzeho".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'Ibikorwa byahuje Ubushinwa riyobowe na OMS ryaratangiye; rigamije gutanga abakozi b'inzobere mpuzamahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo gufasha mu gucunga no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'indwara" binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'igihugu zibishinzwe no gukora ingendo zo ku butaka kugira ngo harebwe "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo guhangana ku rwego rw'intara n'akarere, bigizwe n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi ikeneye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura guhangana n'iki cyorezo cya coronavirus" ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane kugira ngo cyitwe icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba gukomeza "kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyateye imbere muri Irani, OMS yoherejeyo Itsinda ry'Ibikorwa Rihuriweho kugira ngo risuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyiciro cy'ibyago bya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi kizazamurwa kiva ku "cyinshi" kijya ku "cyinshi cyane", iki kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cyo kubanza kugenzura no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mu itangazo Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'umuryango w'abibumbye y'ubuvuzi, yatanze, yatanze umuburo ugira uti "iki ni cyo gihe kugira ngo ubutegetsi bwose bwo ku isi bujye buhura n'ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi: Nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuza mu gihugu cyanyu kandi mugomba kuba mwiteguye", asaba ko ingamba zo guhangana nazo zifatika zafasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adashobora gutuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ibyo bisobanura ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'iyo virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa WHO yavuze ko WHO "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'umubare uteye impungenge w'ikwirakwira n'uburemere, ndetse n'umubare uteye impungenge wo kutagira icyo ikora".WHO yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yananiwe guhangana n'icyorezo, harimo no gutinda gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'indwara y'uburwayi bw'abaturage no gushyira virusi mu byiciro by'icyorezo.
Imwe mu myigaragambyo ikomeye irimo ubusabe bwashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku ya 6 Mata, bugenewe umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom asaba ko yegura.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere nyinshi mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zashimangiye ko uburenganzira bw'umuntu wese bugomba kubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Iri tsinda ry'impuguke rivuga ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira bwo kugira icyo akora kugira ngo akize ubuzima bwe kandi ko leta ari yo ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba gukoreshwa nk'impamvu yo kuvangura itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaza ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, hakubiyemo abamugaye, abanyamuryango b'imiryango mito, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, abari mu mazu y'imbohe, impunzi n'andi matsinda akeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe ubutegetsi irimo gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo ibashe guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage z'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere watangije gahunda yo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ku buryo ibihugu byo ku isi byose byitabira politiki, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'igenzurwa ry'akarere n'ibihano ku ngendo, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga kirimo Urukurikirane rw'ingamba z'igihugu, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwitoza no koroshya uburyo bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenze cyane Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ibiro bya Kabine w'Ubwongereza, Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kubera uburyo bakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi bo mu ntara z'ishyaka rya Kominisiti y'Ubushinwa (CPC) bahagaritswe ku bijyanye n'uburyo ibikorwa byo guhagarika abantu mu Bushinwa bwo hagati byakozwe, mu kugaragaza ko batishimiye uburyo inzego za politiki zagiye zitabira guhangana n'icyorezo muri ako karere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko iyi ntambwe igamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, bahakanye ibyatangajwe mbere ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'ubuhotozi ko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Amerika bwa Donald Trump bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan" buvuga ko "ibikorwa by'Ubushinwa byo guhisha byahaye imbaraga virusi ubu imaze kuba icyorezo ku isi".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyabonye ubutumwa bwa leta ya Amerika bugaragaza uburyo bwo gutumanaho kandi bigaragara ko bwaturutse mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, aho iyo gahunda yasubiwemo ko ari "Ibyerekeye Ubushinwa.
Twabwiwe kugerageza no gutanga ubu butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'amateraniro y'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo".Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko ibikorwa by'Ubushinwa byo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari bimwe mu bikorwa by'ubucuruzi bwo guharabika isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi Josep Borrell, yatanze umuburo ko hari "igice cya geo-politike, gikubiyemo intambara yo gushaka kwigwizaho imbaraga binyuze mu guhinduranya ibintu no 'gukora politiki y'ubuntu.'"
Borrell kandi yavuze ko, "Ubushinwa bufite imbaraga zo gutanga ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufasha ushoboye kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi ko Amerika yakuyeho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse bivugwa ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 yagenewe Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika na bo bashinjwa ko bahindura imfashanyo zigenewe ibindi bihugu bakajya bazishyira mu bihugu byabo.
Hari kandi amakimbirane ajyanye n'udupfukamunwa yavuzwe hagati y'ibindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Autriche n'u Busuwisi; ndetse na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe imashini amagana z'ubuhumekero zari zigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yanenze ko EU itari ifite ubufatanye n'u Butaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwashubije ku buryo bw'impande zombi.
Birumvikana ko ibyo bidatanga ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'i Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kwakira telefoni ya Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yasabye ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza abakozi b'igisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo guhumanya indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo "isoko rikomeye rya politiki" ritavuzwe amazina, rivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Burusiya "nta cyo zimaze cyangwa nta cyo zimaze ku Butaliyani".
Uwo mushinjacyaha yavuze ko u Burusiya bwakoze igitero cy'ubwiza "bw'isi n'ubw'ububanyi n'amahanga".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, n'Umunyamabanga w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi Di Maio birengagije ibyo bitangazamakuru byavuze maze bagaragaza ko bashimiye.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege y'ubwishingizi irimo imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yavuze ko "igihe [Putin] yatangaga ubufasha ku bakozi bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, yafashe umwanzuro w'uko niba abashinzwe ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi byo muri Amerika bahawe amahirwe, na bo bashoboraga kubibasubiza bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ikomeye cyane ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubukonje irangiye, izaba ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 ati "Muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, iyi myitozo ntabwo ihungabanya ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika gusa n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bitabiriye, ahubwo kandi n'abaturage b'ibihugu bakoreramo". Guverinoma ya Irani yibasiwe cyane na virusi, aho abadepite bagera kuri makumyabiri banduye hamwe n'abanyapolitiki cumi na batanu b'ubu cyangwa ba mbere.
Ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye ibaruwa ifunguye abayobozi b'isi asaba ubufasha avuga ko igihugu cye kigorwa no kurwanya icyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga bitewe n'ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika isaba gufata politiki y'imibereho myiza nk'uko bimeze mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo kwivuza kuri bose, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango uhembwa, n'amafaranga menshi yo kwivuza.
Abasesengura politiki batekereza ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorerwa kuyobora igihugu mu matora ya 2020. Imibanire y'ububanyi n'amahanga hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yaragabanutse kubera iki cyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'Ubuyapani yo gushyira abantu mu kato idafite ishingiro kandi idafite icyo ivuze" nyuma y'aho Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uza aturutse muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri ahantu hateganyijwe na leta.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku birebana n'igisubizo Perezida Moon Jae-in yatanze kuri iki kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko, basaba ko Moon acibwa, bashingiye ku byo bavuga ko leta yakoze nabi mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa se bashimira uburyo yabyitabiriye.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko bafite impungenge ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bwongera imbaraga mu butegetsi.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye kureka Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, akajya ku butegetsi mu buryo buhoraho, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora rusange, no guhana abantu bakekwaho gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi no ku buryo leta itegura ibibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ibibazo by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, biturutse ku kwiyongera kw'ibikoresho ku isi byose byo kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhangayika, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyatanze umuburo ku birebana n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abakiriya bifuza cyane kandi abaguzi bakaba batabasha kubikora.
Nanone kandi, mu duce tumwe na tumwe hari ibicuruzwa by'abantu bari mu mimerere yo kwiheba, bituma habaho ubukene bw'ibintu by'ibanze, urugero nk'ibyokurya, amasahani yo mu bwiherero n'amazi yo mu bibindi, bigatuma habaho ubukene.
By'umwihariko, inganda z'ikoranabuhanga zagabishije ku bijyanye n'ibihombo byo gutwara ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom abivuga, ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho byo kwirinda byiyongereye incuro 100.
Ibi byateje kuzamuka kw'ibiciro bikubye inshuro makumyabiri ibiciro bisanzwe ndetse binatuma ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bihagarara mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Ibi kandi bituma ku isi hose habura ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kandi OMS iraburira ko bishobora guteza akaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abaguzi ba daigou babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye amata y'imishongi aba make mu maduka manini ndetse amaherezo abuzwa na leta ya Australia. Nubwo umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ari mwinshi mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo by'ibiribwa biri hejuru, utwo duce tubiri twarahuye n'ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba z'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani mu kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibintu by'ingenzi zagize icyo zigeraho bituma ibura ry'ibiribwa rikomeye riteganyijwe mu Burayi na Amerika ya Ruguru ridakorwa.
Ubutaliyani bw'amajyaruguru, bufite umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi, ntibwigeze bugabanuka cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko byemezwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Amaterasi y'ibiribwa yabaye imfabusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa barimo kurekura ibyangombwa by'inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani, hari itegeko nk'iryo risaba abacuruzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibyokurya mu gihe habaye impanuka nk'iyo.
Impanuka y'ubukungu ku isi yumvikanye mu Bushinwa: nk'uko amakuru yo ku wa 16 Werurwe abivuga, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka mbi mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 bitewe n'ingamba zafashwe na leta zo guhashya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwahise bugabanukaho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bwo ku mugabane w'isi ari ihuriro rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyatangiye gufatwa nk'icyateje akaga gakomeye ku bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubutasi cyitwa Economist Intelligence Unit, atekereza ko isoko rizakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe hazabaho igishushanyo cyiza cy'umusaruro ushobora kuzagerwaho.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu by'inganda batangaje ko ingaruka z'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ryaturutse ku cyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke zo muri kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, zivuga ko ibyorezo by'indwara byangiza ibintu bisaga miriyari 300 z'amadolari ku isoko ry'ibiribwa ku isi, bikaba bishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitanga peteroli (OPEC) wavuzwe ko "wagize ubwoba" nyuma y'uko ibiciro bya peteroli byagabanutse cyane kubera ko ubukene bwari bwararaga bugabanutse buvuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yaguye kubera ubwiyongere bukomeye bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo bitandukanye by'imigabane ya Amerika, birimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500 Index, na Dow Jones Industrial Average, byanditse kugabanuka kwabyo guhambaye kuva mu 2008, Dow igeze ku manota 1,191, igabanuka ry'umunsi umwe rinini cyane kuva mu makuba y'imari yo mu 20072008.
Imibare itatu y'imigabane yarangiye icyumweru igabanutseho 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje indangagaciro y'inguzanyo ya leta y'Ubushinwa, ariko ikomeza kugira icyizere ko izakemuka.
Imicungire y'imigabane yongeye kugwa kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, igabanuka rikomeye ryabaye ku ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu bw'isi bugiye guhungabana.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba za leta n'iz'ibiro bikuru z'igihugu zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Banki nkuru z'igihugu zagize icyo zikora vuba cyane kurusha uko zabikoze mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'amafaranga mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu bice byahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye kubera amategeko abuza ingendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu ho gusura, n'ingamba za leta zo kugabanya ingendo ku isi.
Ibyo byatumye ingendo z'indege nyinshi zihagarikwa kubera ko hari abantu bake cyane, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe ingendo z'indege zo mu karere k'Ubwongereza Flybe zaguye.
Ingaruka ku bucuruzi bw'amato y'ubwato zigeze ku rwego rutagereranywa.
Ibigo bimwe na bimwe by'indarayi n'ibibuga by'amato na byo byafunzwe.
Icyorezo cyahuriranye na Chunyun, igihe cy'ingenzi cy'ingendo kijyanye n'ikiruhuko cy'Umwaka Mushya wa Lunar.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'abantu benshi byahagaritswe na guverinoma nkuru n'intara, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka by'umwaka mushya wa Lunar, kandi ibigo byigenga na byo byiteguye gufunga amaduka n'ahantu hakurura ba mukerarugendo, nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'umwaka mushya wa Lunar n'ahantu nyaburanga byafunzwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda amakoraniro y'abantu benshi, harimo n'Umujyi Wambuwe i Beijing n'ibirori by'urusengero gakondo.
Mu ntara 24, mu mijyi 31 n'uturere, abategetsi bongereye ikiruhuko cy'Umwaka Mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare kandi bategeka ko imirimo myinshi itazongera gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice bitanga 80% bya GDP y'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yazamuriye ingamba zo kurwanya indwara zandura ku rwego rwo hejuru kandi itangaza ibihe bidasanzwe, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe, kandi ihagarika ibirori by'Umwaka Mushya. Uruganda rw'ubucuruzi rwagize ingaruka ku isi hose kubera kugabanya amasaha y'akazi cyangwa gufunga by'agateganyo.
Gusura abacuruzi mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo byagabanutseho 40%.
Abacuruzi bo muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bari ku gipimo cya 50% na 60%.
Ibi kandi byatumye imodoka z'abanyamaguru zigenda ku isoko zigabanukaho 33-43% muri Werurwe ugereranyije na Gashyantare.
Abafite ibigo by'ubucuruzi hirya no hino ku isi bashyizeho ingamba zinyuranye, nko kongera isuku, gushyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe byo kugenzura ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi, no guhagarika ibikorwa. Nk'uko Komisiyo y'ubukungu ya Loni ku bihugu bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo ibyerekana, ubukene buterwa n'icyorezo bushobora gutuma abantu bari mu bukene bukabije muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo biyongera hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze mbere y'icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bo mu cyaro bo mu Bushinwa bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bataye ingo zabo mu ntara yo hagati cyangwa bagatabwa muri Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi maze basaba ubufasha bwa leta.
Nk'uko byemezwa na Banki Nkuru y'Igihugu ya St. Louis, icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutuma abantu miliyoni 47 batakaza akazi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%. Gushyira mu kato mu turere two mu Buhinde byatumye abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde babarirwa muri za miriyoni mirongo (bishyurwa binyuze mu mishahara ya buri munsi) batagira akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo Angus Reid Institute bwagaragaje ko 44% by'ingo zo muri Kanada zabuze akazi.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi bagera kuri miliyoni 4 b'Abafaransa basabye inyungu z'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo n'abakozi miliyoni 1 b'Abongereza basabye gahunda y'inguzanyo rusange.
Ingamba z'indishyi z'akazi k'igihe gito z'Abadage zashyizweho n'Abafaransa n'Abongereza.
Ku isi hose, ibikorwa by'ubuhanzi n'umurage byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango n'abantu, baba abikorera cyangwa abikorera.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yihatira gushyigikira inshingano zabo (akenshi zitangwa n'abaturage) zo kugeza umurage w'umuco ku baturage, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi n'abaturage, no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose no ku rwego rutandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, ibitabo, ibigo by'imyidagaduro n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byafunzwe igihe kitarambiranye, hamwe n'imurika, ibitaramo n'ibitaramo byahagaritswe cyangwa byasubitswe.
Mu gusubiza, hakozwe imbaraga nyinshi zo gutanga serivisi zindi binyuze mu buryo bwa digitale. Ikindi kintu kibi cyatewe n'iki cyorezo gishya kandi kiri kwiyongera vuba ni ukuhagarika serivisi z'idini, ibirori bikomeye by'imikino, n'ibindi birori by'imibanire, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga, ndetse n'imurikabikorwa ry'imideri.
Ikigo cya Vatikani cyatangaje ko ibirori byo mu cyumweru gitagatifu i Roma, byabaga mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igisibo cy'abakristo bahindukiriye idini, byahagaritswe.
Amadini menshi ategeka Abakristo bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu ngo zabo kandi ntibasange Misa ku Cyumweru; amadini amwe n'amwe atanga amasengesho y'itorero kuri radiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo, mu gihe andi atanga amasengesho yo mu modoka cyangwa ku karubanda.
Kubera ko Kiliziya Gatolika ya Roma yafunze insengero n'insengero zayo kandi ikimura abakirisitu mu Kibuga cya Petero, izindi nzego z'amadini na zo zahagaritse imirimo no kugabanya amateraniro y'abantu mu nsengero, mu nsengero, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no mu masengero.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yahagaritswe mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo kandi ko insengero zafunzwe, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abagenzi b'abanyamahanga n'abaturage kwinjira mu nsengero za Mecca na Medina.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane ku ngengabihe y'imikino ku isi kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Imikino myinshi ikomeye yahagaritswe cyangwa ihagarikwa, harimo UEFA Champions League 2019-2020, Premier League 2019-2020, UEFA Euro 2020, NBA 2019-2020, na NHL 2019-2020.
