Perezida w'ishyaka rya Bharatiya Janata mu ntara ya Bengal, Dilip Ghosh, yavuze ko Ubushinwa bwarimbuye ibidukikije kandi "ni yo mpamvu Imana yabahaye igihano".
Ayo magambo yaje kwamagwa n'ikigo cy'ubuserukizi bw'Ubushinwa i Kolkata, avuga ko "ari ibinyoma".Mu Bushinwa, urwikekwe rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura ku baturage batari Abashinwa byaragabanutse kubera icyorezo, abanyamahanga bagaragazwa nk'"ibishingwe by'abanyamahanga" kandi bagashyirwa ku "buji".
