Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura ko virusi iriho kandi bugaragaza ko hari abanduye iyo virusi.
Kuba virusi yari mu cyitegererezo byemejwe na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Ibizamini ni umwihariko kandi byateguriwe gutahura RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 yonyine.
Ibi bizamini bikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyangwa bukiriho.
Kumenya ibimenyetso by'abanduye (serologie) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu bamaze kwandura, bigasobanura abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batabivuga cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso.
Imibare nyayo y'impfu ziterwa n'indwara n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa bw'itsinda mu baturage bishobora kumenyekana biturutse ku bisubizo by'ibizamini.
Kubera ko ibizamini ari bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibipimo ibihugu byakoze.
Ibi bishobora no kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'urupfu rw'abanduye, ishobora kuba ari myinshi cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), ubu bushakashatsi bushobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe n'uburyo butandukanye, harimo no guhanagura mu mazuru cyangwa ibipimo by'amahembe.
Ubusanzwe, ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Ibizamini bya RT-PCR bikorwa ku mukondo w'izuru ni byo byiringirwa gusa mu byumweru bya mbere by'indwara.
Nyuma, virusi ishobora kugenda mu muhogo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ubundi, ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibipimo bishobora gutorwa mu mwuka w'imbere hifashishijwe indobo yo mu mwenge cyangwa ibintu byasohotse binyuze mu guhoberana (umwanda) bishobora gukoreshwa.
Imwe mu ngero za mbere za PCR yakozwe i Charité, Berlin, muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje imikorere y'uruziga rwa polymerase mu gihe cy'igihe cy'ukuri (rRT-PCR), kandi yashyizeho ibikoresho by'igerageza bigera ku 250,000 bizatangwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwashyizeho igerageza ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020.Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Kogenebiotech cyashyizeho ikoranabuhanga ryo gupima SARS-CoV-2 rishingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku rwego rw'ubuvuzi ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Iki gikoresho gishakisha ingirabuzima fatizo "E" zigaragazwa na za koronavirusi zose za beta, n'ingirabuzima fatizo RdRp zigaragaza SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni kimwe mu bigo bya mbere byahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ibikoresho by'Ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ku bikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatanze Urupapuro rw'Igenzura rwa RT-PCR rw'Igihe Nyakuri rw'Igisubizo cya Coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) mu bigo by'ubuvuzi rusange binyuze mu Kigo Mpuzamahanga cy'Ibikoresho.
Kimwe mu bipimo bitatu bya jenoside mu bipimo bya kera bitanga ibisubizo bidahamye kubera ikosa ry'imiti, kandi umubare w'ibipimo muri CDC i Atlanta ni muto; ibi byatumye ku kigereranyo ibipimo bikeya 100 ku munsi bikorwa neza muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri byafashwe nk'ibidashoboka kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, hanyuma ni bwo laboratoire za leta n'iz'aho zemeye gukora ibizamini.
Iki cyemezo cyemejwe n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (FDA) ku buryo bw'ibanze.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko hari gukorwa ibizamini bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR ku rwego rw'igihugu.
Byongeye kandi, Quest Diagnostics yatumye ibizamini bya COVID-19 biboneka mu gihugu cyose ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta gihagararo cy'ubwinshi cyatangajwe; gukusanya no gutunganya ibipimo bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ibizamini bya COVID-19 byakozwe kandi bikorerwa mu kigo cya Leta cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubwandu n'ikoranabuhanga VECTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe na Federal Service for Surveilance in Healthcare. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko irimo gukora ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 ku gipimo kinini ku buryo imashini imwe ishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) ku bigo by'ubushakashatsi bya Abbott Laboratories kugirango bikore ibizamini kuri m2000 Abbott system; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo kuri Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid kandi yahawe EUA na FDA mu igerageza ryamaze iminota igera kuri 45.
FDA yemeje ibizamini bikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingufu za nucleic acid mu buryo butari PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ko habaho imikino y'ihindagurika ry'ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu minota itanu gusa n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Ubu hari ibyuma bigera ku 18,000 muri Amerika, Abbott iteganya kongera umusaruro kugeza ku bipimo 50,000 ku munsi.Ibisubizo bikoresha umuti wa monoclonal wifatanya na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (poroteyine N) ya coronavirus nshya biri gukorwa muri Taiwan, byitezwe gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'ibipimo bya mbere bya grippe.
Isesengura ry'ibitabo ryanditswe mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020 ryavuze ko "amafoto y'igituza afite agaciro gake mu gusuzuma indwara mu gihe cy'ibanze, mu gihe ibipimo bya CT [computed tomography] bishobora kuba byarabonetse mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira".
Ibintu biranga CT birimo umubyimba wa vitre-glass mu buryo bw'impande zombi, ufite imiterere y'impande, itandukanye n'iy'inyuma.
Imyinshi mu miterere y'iyo ndwara, ni ubwiyongere bw'ubwonko, kandi ikomeza kwiyongera uko indwara igenda ikura.
I Wuhan, ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije PCR na CT mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'iki gihe, bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ibyiyumvo byinshi kurusha PCR, nubwo idasanzwe, kuko hari ibintu byinshi byo kwifotoza bibangikanye n'indwara ya Pneumonia n'izindi ndwara.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imirase cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza rya mbere mu gupima COVID-19". Muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yatanze inama yo gukoresha PCR mu gupima mbere.
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'umubiri ku cyorezo ni ugushinga za 'antibodies' zirimo IgM na IgG.
Bishobora gukoreshwa mu gutahura ubwandu mu bantu kuva mu minsi 7 nyuma yo gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso, mu kumenya ubudahangarwa ku ndwara, no mu kugenzura abaturage.
Sisitemu zigezweho zigezweho mu mavuriro menshi zizashobora gukora ubu bushakashatsi, ariko kuboneka kwazo bizaterwa n'urwego rw'ikoranabuhanga kuri buri sisitemu.
Ku CLT, byibanze hakoreshwa icyitegererezo kimwe cyamaraso yo ku mpande, nubwo icyiciro cy'ibipimo gishobora gukoreshwa gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri.
Ku bw'ubu buryo bwa PoCT, hakoreshwa urugero rumwe rw'amaraso y'uruhande rw'umubiri avanywe mu gitsina.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, intambwe yo gukuramo ntiisabwa mbere yo gusuzuma. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yavuze ibigo 29 bitanga imenyekanisha ku kigo nk'uko bikenewe kandi rero ubu bishobora gutanga ibizamini byabo by'abanduye.
Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, hari ikigo kimwe gusa cyemejwe na FDA ku buryo bw'ibanze. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics bahawe uburenganzira bw'Uburayi ku bikoresho byabo by'igerageza bishobora gutahura antibody za IgG na IgA kuri virusi mu cyitegererezo cy'amaraso.
Ishobora gupima ibipimo amagana mu masaha make, bityo ikaba yihuta cyane kurusha PCR isanzwe isuzuma RNA ya virusi.
Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwabonye ko nta gikoresho na kimwe cy'isuzuma cy'abanduye cyagaragaye ko gifite ubushobozi bwo gukoresha.
Hong Kong yashyizeho gahunda yo kureka abarwayi bakekwaho indwara bagasigara mu rugo, "ishami ry'ubutabazi rizaha abarwayi udupira tw'ibipimo", bakaza kubirohamo, bakazisubiza, bakabona ibisubizo nyuma y'igihe gito. NHS y'Ubwongereza yatangaje ko NHS iri gutangiza gahunda yo gupima abarwayi bakekwaho indwara mu rugo bityo bikagabanya ibyago byo kwanduza abandi abarwayi niba baje kwa muganga cyangwa bagomba kuvura ambulansi iyo ikoreshejwe. Mu gupima ku butaka ku bantu bakekwaho COVID-19, umukozi w'ubuzima uzatoranya ibipimo akoresheje ingamba zikwiriye.
Ikigo cy'ibizamini bya lantur cyatumye Koreya y'Epfo ikora ibizamini byihuse kandi byinshi kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose. Ku ya 2 Werurwe, Ishyirahamwe ry'Igihugu ry'Abaganga b'Ubuzima bw'Ubuzima bwemewe n'amategeko mu Budage ryavuze ko Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bigera ku 12.000 ku munsi mu rwego rwo kwa muganga kandi ko ibizamini 10.700 byakozwe mu cyumweru gishize.
Ibiciro byishyurwa n'ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima iyo ibizamini byasabwe n'umuganga.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi w'ikigo Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 160.000 buri cyumweru.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, ibizamini byo gupima ikibanza byatangirijwe mu mijyi minini.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzwi kuko hari raporo z'ibisubizo byiza gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'urwego rw'ibanze bwagaragaje ko, mu gihe cyose, nibura ibipimo 483,295 byasuzumwe kugeza no mu cyumweru cya 12/2020 kandi ibipimo 33,491 (6,9%) byasuzumwe neza kuri SARS-CoV-2. Muri Isirayeli, abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam bahimbye kandi bapima uburyo bwo gupima ibipimo by'abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, bafatanya ibipimo kandi bagakora ibindi bipimo gusa iyo ibipimo by'ibipimo byasanganwe neza. Muri Wuhan, ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi bw'imiterere y'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo byitwa "Huo-Yan" (Mandarin: 火眼, cyangwa "Amaso y'umuriro" mu rurimi rw'ikinyandoneziya) cyatangijwe ku ya 5 Gashyantare 2020 na BGI, gishobora gutunganya ibipimo birenga 10,000 ku munsi.
Kubera ko yubatswe n'uwatangije BGI Wang Jian kandi bikaba byaratwaye iminsi itanu, imiterere yerekana ko ubwandu muri Hubei bushobora kuba 47% hejuru kandi ibiciro bijyanye no gukemura ikibazo cy'igenzura bishobora kwiyongera kabiri niba ubu bushobozi bwo gupima butabaho.
Laboratwari ya Wuhan yahise ikurikirwa na Huo-Yan laboratwari i Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing, na Shanghai, mu mijyi 12 yose yo mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, ubushobozi busesuye bwa buri munsi ni ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi. Igishushanyo mbonera cy'isoko rusange cyasohotse na Origami Assays gishobora gupima ibipimo by'abarwayi 1,222 kuri COVID-19 hakoreshejwe ibizamini 93 gusa.
Kugeza muri Werurwe, ibura n'ibura ry'ibikoresho byagenewe gupima byabaye imbogamizi mu gupima abantu benshi mu Burayi, mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, abashakashatsi bamwe na bamwe bagerageje gukora ubushakashatsi ku buryo bwo gutegura ibipimo bikubiyemo gushyushya ibipimo kuri 98 °C (208 °F) mu gihe cy'iminota 5 kugira ngo batange ADN ya RNA kugira ngo isuzumwe kurushaho. Ku ya 31 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu zavuzwe ko zikora ibizamini byinshi bya coronavirus ku muturage umwe kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose, kandi ziteguye kongera ibipimo byo gupima kugirango zigere ku gice kinini cy'abaturage.
Ibi byakozwe binyuze mu guhuza ibizamini byo ku butaka no kugura laboratwari z'ibanze z'ibanze z'abaturage bo mu itsinda rya 42 na BGI (ishingiye ku kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi bw'imiti cyo mu Bushinwa "Huo-Yan").
Yubatswe mu minsi 14, ishobora gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR bibarirwa mu bihumbi mirongo ku munsi kandi ni laboratwari ya mbere iri kuri ubu rwego hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ibikoresho bitandukanye byo gupima bibangamira ibice bitandukanye by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bya coronavirus byatangiye gukorwa mu Bushinwa, u Bufaransa, u Budage, Hong Kong, u Buyapani na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyize mu bikorwa amabwiriza y'u Budage yo gukora ibikoresho byo gupima, byoherezwa mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, bidafite ubushobozi bwo kubyikorera.
Itegeko ry'u Budage ryasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; amabwiriza y'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara ntabwo yabonetse kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama bityo bigabanya ibipimo biboneka muri Amerika. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, Ubushinwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byagize ibibazo ku kwizerwa kw'ibikoresho byo gupima; ibi bihugu byombi na Ositaraliya ntibyashoboraga gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byo gupima ngo bihuze ibyifuzo n'inama z'abaganga.
Ahubwo, impuguke zivuga ko kuba muri Koreya y'Epfo hari ibipimo byinshi bifasha kugabanya ikwirakwira rya koronavirusi nshya.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima, ahanini mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi by'abikorera, bwubatswe mu myaka mike na leta ya Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko gahunda yo gupima yongerwa nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19. Ibisabwa byinshi byo gupima kubera ikwirakwira rya virusi byatumye ibihumbi amagana by'ibizamini bitegereza gukorwa mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi byigenga byo muri Amerika, kandi ibicuruzwa by'ibikoresho byo guhanagura hamwe n'ibikoresho by'imiti byabaye ingenzi.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari ikibazo cy'ubuziranenge mu bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ibikoresho by'ibizamini byakozwe na CDC byari bifite "amakosa"; leta yaje gukuraho inzitizi z'ibiro by'ubuyobozi byatumaga ibizamini bitemewe n'abikorera.
Iryo shyirahamwe ryasobanuye ko ibisubizo bitari byo bishobora guterwa n'ubushobozi buke bwo gukusanya ibipimo cyangwa gukoresha neza ibikoresho byo gupima.
Minisiteri ya Espagne yavuze ko igiye guhagarika ibikoresho bitanga ibisubizo bitari byo, ikabisimbuza ibindi bikoresho by'ibizamini bitangwa na Shenzhen Bioeasy. 80% by'ibikoresho by'ibizamini byaguzwe n'igihugu cya Czech Republic bivuye mu Bushinwa bitanga ibisubizo bitari byo. Slovakia yaguze ibikoresho by'ibizamini miriyoni 1,2 bivuye mu Bushinwa byagaragaye ko bitari byo.
