Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko kongera imikoreshereze yo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abana bato barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'indwara z'ibinyigishi ushobora kugabanuka binyuze mu guhindura imyitwarire yoroheje, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo myifatire yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara ugera hafi kuri 50%.
Iterambere rishishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki rishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara ya diarrhée ho kimwe cya gatatu; rishobora gukorwa binyuze mu gutanga amazi meza mu duce dukennye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'ibipimo by'indwara ya diarrhée bishobora kwitirirwa gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bumwe rukumbi bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda diarrhée n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ISPA), nk'uko imyitwarire idasanzwe ikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Pneumonia, ari na yo mpamvu y'ibanze ituma abana bapfa, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere ihitana abana bakiri bato; buri mwaka ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8.
