Ingaruka mbi zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu bitewe no kumeneka.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 muri Danemark bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera ikibazo cy'uruhu rurimo umunyu n'ibihuha, bizwi ku izina rya eczema y'intoki cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, cyane cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo bigaragara nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'ubushake bwo guhaza irari ry'umubiri (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu bikomeye mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibinure, ari byo: mbere na nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gukorora, gusama), nyuma yo gusukura umugongo w'umwana (guhindura indabo), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gutunganya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Indi mimerere y'ingenzi yo gukoresha uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki mu kwirinda kwandura indwara ni mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku gikomere; nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorakora inyamaswa; no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki n'isabune biracyari hasi cyane.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo ingo 38,7% zikora isuku y'intoki n'isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru ku kigero cya 97 ku ijana; Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziri hafi hagati ku kigero cya 77 ku ijana; n'u Bushinwa bufite igipimo cyo hasi ku kigero cya 23 ku ijana. Ubu hari uburyo butandukanye bwo guhindura imyitwarire buboneka bwo kongera umuco wo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihe bikomeye.
