Iyo usukura, amazi yo mu ntoki zawe hasi agomba guhagarikwa kugira ngo atazongera gutemba mu ntoki.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba intoki, bazisahura umwenda wanduye kandi bambare ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo utagenda wiruka, ni byiza ko ukaraba intoki cyangwa ugakoresha umuti wica udukoko mbere na nyuma yo gukora ku muntu urwaye.
Ku bijyanye no kugenzura indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu zikomeye zo gukaraba intoki zituruka ku masaha 20 ku ijana yo gukaraba intoki, kandi ko inyungu zinyuranye zigaragara iyo umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki wiyongereye hejuru ya 35 ku ijana.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe bitera kwandura indwara ziterwa n'imirire inshuro zirenga eshatu ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune ikoreshwa n'imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'isukari n'isabune ikoreshwa n'imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara n'igihe cya kabiri cy'amasegonda 30 buri kimwe kigaragaza ko gukaraba intoki n'isukari bigabanya ubwandu bw'indwara ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune ikoreshwa n'imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara.
Ariko, isabune n'amazi bifite ingaruka nziza kurusha imiti yo gusukura intoki ishingiye ku nzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya influenza A H1N1 na Clostridium difficile ku ntoki.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwinshi kugira ngo tumenye uburyo bwiza bwo kuvura mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabuni byemewe ko ari uburyo bw'ibanze kandi buhendutse bwo kugera ku buzima bwiza ndetse no ku mirire myiza.
Icyakora, kuba abantu badafite amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo zabo, mu mashuri no mu kazi, bituma kugera ku ntego yo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose biba ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro byo muri Afurika, nta bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki biri hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa ubw'abaturage biboneka, nubwo hari uburyo bwo gukora ahantu ho gukaraba intoki hato.
Icyakora, kuba umuntu adakaraba intoki neza bishobora guterwa n'akamenyero yari afite, aho guterwa n'ibura ry'isabune cyangwa amazi.
Gushishikariza no gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku ngingo zifatwa mu rwego rwa politiki, bikongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu bahindura imyitwarire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo bigende neza, hakenewe kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Isesengura ryakozwe ku buryo buhoraho ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku muryango ari bwo bw'ingirakamaro mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite amikoro make, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza ku mibereho y'abaturage butari bufite ingaruka nziza.
Iyo ibisabwa by'ibanze byubahirijwe, ishuri rishobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe rikaza kugera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka aho gukarabira intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki kugira ngo bagabanye uburwayi n'urupfu mu bana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo kongera ubumenyi bugamije guhindura imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, UNICEF yashishikarije gukoresha emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe bwagaragaje akamaro ko gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu bijyanye no kwirinda imyaka y'ubuzima ivanze n'ubumuga (Disability-adjusted Life Years, DALY).
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gutera abantu inkunga yo gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune ari byo bifite akamaro kurusha ibindi bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki n'amazi.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu, cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo, urugero nk'umugore wabyaye cyangwa umusirikare wakomerekeye mu bitaro, kavumbuwe bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 rwagati n'abantu babiri bari bashyigikiye isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umuhungariya witwaga Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, na Florence Nightingale, "washyizeho ubuvuzi bwa none" mu Bwongereza.
Icyo gihe, abantu benshi bari bacyizera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi y'umwuka.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo by'indwara zandurira mu biribwa n'indwara ziterwa n'ubuvuzi byatumye Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gihamagarira abantu kugira isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byateje impungenge mu bihugu byinshi ku kamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
Urugero, hari ibyapa byanditseho amagambo agira ati "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki" byamanitswe iruhande rw'imisegetera yo gukaraba intoki mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'amazu y'ibiro n'amazu y'indege mu Budage.
Amagambo ngo "kwirinda" ikintu, yumvikanisha ko umuntu yanga kugira uruhare mu kintu runaka cyangwa se kugifatanyamo.
Iyo mvugo yavuye mu nkuru yo muri Bibiliya yanditswe na Matayo, ivuga uko Ponsiyo Pilato yakosoye intoki ze igihe yafataga umwanzuro wo kumanika Yesu Kristo, ariko yaje gukoreshwa cyane mu Bwongereza.
Mu gitabo cya Shakespeare, Macbeth, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ze buri gihe kugira ngo akureho ibizinga byo mu bitekerezo; igikorwa kigaragaza icyaha yakoze kandi cyatumye umugabo we abikora.
Byaramenyekanye kandi ko, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, abantu barushaho gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi bakishimira cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza batyo ntibaba bafite amahirwe menshi yo gukora ibikorwa byo kwishyura "gukuraho", nko gukora nk'abakorerabushake.
Amadini ategeka gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, hakoreshejwe amazi, ariko nta isabune yo gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki mu madini menshi, harimo Aba Baha'i, Abahindu, Twila na Netilat yadayim mu Buyuda, Lavabo mu Bukristo, na Wudhu muri Islam.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu basabwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero.
Byongeye kandi, Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu basabwa gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya.
Gutegeka akaga ko mu kazi ka COVID-19
Gucunga akaga mu kazi ka COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukumira akaga mu kazi mu kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza akaga mu kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'akazi akora, bishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago by'aho ahurira n'indwara, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'uko umukozi ashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi k'ibyago byo guhura n'ibicurane gafite aho gaherereye gafite aho gaherereye gafite aho gaherereye gaherereye mu kazi gaherereye mu baturage n'abandi bakozi; ku kazi nk'ako, higanje ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, zirimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, amahame mbwirizamuco yo guhumeka, no gukora isuku no guhumanya ibidukikije ku kazi.
Akazi k'ibyago byo kwandura mu buryo bworoshye gakubiyemo akazi gasabwa guhura cyane cyangwa kenshi n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Iri tsinda ririmo abakozi bahuye n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abaturage benshi, n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwinshi.
Gutegeka akaga kuri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, birimo guhumeka ukoresheje imashini z'umwuka zikora neza, kurinda gusinzira no gutanga ibikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi b'ubuzima n'abakora mu byumba by'abapfuye bagaragarijwe abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 ko bafite ibyago byo kwandura, bikazamuka bikajya ku kigero cyo kurwara cyane iyo abakozi bakoze uburyo bwo gukora aerosol ku bantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, cyangwa batwaye cyangwa bakoreye ibizamini ku bantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Gutegeka akaga gakwiriye uyu mukozi birimo kugenzura ikoranabuhanga, nk'icyumba cy'umwuka utera umunaniro, n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikwiye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutajya ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu birebana n'ubwoko bw'ibintu bisabwa cyangwa uburyo bwo kubikora (urugero nko guhaha nyuma y'amasaha y'ikiruhuko, binyuze mu kohereza ibintu cyangwa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere tuzwiho kuba twugarijwe na COVID-19 bishobora guhungabana. Imyiteguro n'imigambi yo guhangana n'indwara zandura bishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ingamba zo kwirinda.
Gahunda igena igipimo cy'ibyago bijyanye n'aho umuntu akorera n'akazi akora, ikagaragaza aho abonera ibyago, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye, nk'imyaka cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Iyo gahunda kandi igaragaza ingamba z'ubugenzuzi zikenewe mu guhangana n'ibyo byago n'ingamba zo guhangana n'ibiza bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'icyorezo.
Imyiteguro n'imigambi yo guhangana n'indwara zandura bishobora gukurikiza amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo zirimo kugabanya ubwandu hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zidakira, gukomeza imikorere y'ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo byo mu muyoboro w'itangwa ry'ibiribwa.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi buri bugira ingaruka ku ngamba zo guhangana.
Urwego rwo kugenzura akaga ni urwego rukoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi mu gushyira hamwe ingamba zo kugenzura akaga hashingiwe ku bushobozi bwazo.
Iyo hatari ya COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kuyirinda ni ubuhanga, hakurikiraho ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakurikiraho ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Gutegeka mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga bikubiyemo kugabanya abakozi akaga ko mu kazi, bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'abakozi kandi bishobora kuba umuti mwiza cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Gufata ibyemezo ni ihinduka mu buryo bw'imikorere cyangwa mu buryo bw'imikorere, bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (APD) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza ugereranyije n'ibikorwa by'ubuhanga n'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha kwirinda bimwe mu byo umuntu ashobora guhura na byo.
Ubwoko bwose bwa APD bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga ku mukozi, gushyirwaho neza nk'uko bikwiye (urugero, imashini ihumeka), kwambara neza kandi neza, gusuzumwa, kwitabwaho no gusimbuzwa igihe cyose, niba ari ngombwa, no gukurwaho, gusukura no kubikwa neza cyangwa kujugunywa kugira ngo wirinde kwanduzwa.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi k'ibyago byo guhura n'ibiza gafite aho gafite aho gafite aho gafite guhura n'abantu bake cyane n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zisabwa ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, amahame agenga guhumeka arimo gupfuka ikimwaro no guswera, gutanga utwuma n'ibikoresho byo guhana imyanda, gutegura akazi ko gukorera kure cyangwa guhinduranya amasaha yo kugera/kuva ku kazi, niba ari ngombwa, kubwira abakozi kudakoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukora isuku no guhumanya ibidukikije buri gihe.
Kumenya vuba no gushyira abantu mu kato bashobora kwandura indwara ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kirasaba ko abakozi bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe batagaragayeho umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti itera ibimenyetso, kandi ko politiki y'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara igomba kuba yoroshye ku buryo yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi ko abakozi bamenya aya mabwiriza.
OSHA ivuga ko akazi k'ibyago byo guhura n'ibiza gisanzwe gakubiyemo akazi gashobora gusaba guhura cyane cyangwa kenshi mu ntera ya metero esheshatu n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 kubera ubwandu mu baturage bari hafi y'aho bakorera, cyangwa se kubera ko umuntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Iri tsinda rikubiyemo abakozi bahuye n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, no mu masoko y'ubucuruzi. Gutegeka kwa tekiniki kuri iri tsinda n'itsinda ry'abari mu kaga gukabije birimo gushyiraho filtrateur y'umwuka ikora neza, kongera umuvuduko w'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nka plastike ituma umuntu aswera, no gushyiraho amadirishya yo gutwara imodoka cyangwa ikiraro cyo gukoreramo abakiriya. Gutegeka kwa guverinoma kuri iri tsinda n'itsinda ry'abari mu kaga gakomeye birimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza imibonano ihuza amaso n'imikorere ya virtual, gukora gahunda yo guhinduranya imirimo n'igihe cyo kugera/kuva mu kazi buhoro buhoro, guhagarika ingendo z'abantu batagira akazi ahantu hari icyorezo cya COVID-19, gushyiraho gahunda y'itumanaho ryihutirwa harimo kuvugana n'abakozi, guha abakozi uburezi n'imfashanyamubiri n'imyitwarire y'ubwirinzi, kubamenyereza abakozi gukoresha imyenda n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, kubitaho no guha abakiriya n'abakozi ahantu hakenewe ubufasha bw'ubwisanzure bwo gukora, kubara mu kazi, kwambara udupfukamunwa, indorerwamo, indorerwamo n'ama, cyangwa ibindi bikoresho bikenewe, hamwe n'ibindi.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abashobora guhura n'ingaruka z'iyi ndwara ntibakunze gukenera ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba nziza zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagenzi zirimo gutandukanya umuntu urwaye n'abandi abantu mu ntera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umuntu wo mu bwato wo kwita ku muntu urwaye, no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko apfuka umunwa n'izuru akoresheje agatambaro igihe akoroye cyangwa atetse.
Abakozi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'imiti tw'imishwaro iyo bita ku bagenzi barwaye cyangwa bakora ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kwandura, ndetse wenda n'ibindi bikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe umushoferi urwaye afite umuriro, akomeje gukorora cyangwa afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Inkweto n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka w'ubumara, kandi ibice byanduye bigomba gusukurwa no guhumanywa nyuma. Ku ngendo z'ubucuruzi, harimo amato y'ubwato n'andi mato y'abagenzi, kugenzura akaga birimo gusubika urugendo iyo urwaye, kwigunga, no kumenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo ku bwato ako kanya iyo umuntu afite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana ubuvuzi bikorwa mu byumba by'abantu birimo ubwigunge. Uretse ikwirakwira mu baturage, ku mashuri no mu bigo byita ku bana, CDC irasaba gufunga by'igihe gito kugira ngo hasukurwe cyangwa hakurwemo udukoko turimo udukoko mu gihe umuntu wanduye yaba yarigeze kuba mu nyubako z'ishuri.
Iyo ubwandu mu baturage buri ku kigero cyo hasi kugeza ku gipimo cyo hagati, ingamba zo kugabanya imikorere y'abantu zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, zirimo: guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, inama n'andi materaniro manini, nk'imyitozo ngororamubiri, amasomo ya korali, cyangwa kurya mu kabari, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, igihe cyo kugera no gutaha buhoro buhoro, kugabanya abashyitsi batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho gukorera ibiro by'ubuzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Niba hari ubwandu bwinshi mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda imibanire, kongera gufunga amashuri birashobora gusuzumwa. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora imirimo isanzwe ya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima bwihuse bifatwa ko ari bike na CDC.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'abantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 barasabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi, harimo no kwambara ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Niba habonetse umuntu uhuye na we mu gihe cyo gufatwa, umukozi agomba gusukura no guhanagura udupfunyika n'ibikoresho by'akazi mbere yo kongera kubikoresha akoresheje imashini yo gusukura cyangwa umwanda w'inzu kandi agakurikiza inzira zisanzwe z'imikorere zo kugenzura no gutakaza APD zikoreshwa ndetse no kugenzura no kumesa imyenda imyanda.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu buvuzi n'amazu amwe n'amwe y'abapfuye nk'aho bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Imirimo y'ibyago byinshi ikubiyemo abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima, abafasha, ibigo by'ubushakashatsi n'abakozi bo mu buvuzi bitwara abantu mu modoka bahura n'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Aka kazi kaba gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi cyane mu gihe umukozi akoze imikorere ituma habaho aerosol, cyangwa afashe cyangwa akora ku bipimo by'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Uburyo bwo gukora aerosol burimo guterwa intanga, uburyo bwo gutera inkorora, bronchoscopy, uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo gusuzuma amenyo, cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'ubwandu.
Akazi k'amazu y'ubupfu afite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ubwandu ni akazi gasaba abakozi gutegura imirambo y'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 mu gihe bapfuye; aka kazi kaba gafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ubwandu mu gihe abakozi bakoze autopsies. Ubu buryo bw'inyongera bwo kugenzura iki cyiciro cy'ibyago ni ukwirinda icyumba cyo kwihererana ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, harimo igihe hakorwa uburyo bwo gukora aérosol.
Ibirimo umwuka mubi w'umuvuduko ukabije bishobora kuba byiza mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuvuzi no mu byumba by'abapfuye.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa mu buryo bw'ubwirinzi bw'ibinyabuzima bwo ku rwego rwa 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryasabye ko abarwayi baza bashyirwa mu byumba bitandukanye by'abategereje abantu bashyizwe mu byumba bitandukanye bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Uretse izindi ndwara, OSHA na yo yasabye ko abantu bakorera ku birenge 6 by'umurwayi uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kwandura SARS-CoV-2, n'abantu bakora imikorere ikora kuri aerosol bakoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, udupfukamunwa tw'amaso tw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi twitwa N95 twemewe na NIOSH cyangwa se byiza kurushaho tugomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'igikorwa cy'ubwirinzi bw'ubuhumekero cyanditswe kandi cyuzuye gikubiyemo ibizamini byo kuba bikwiriye, amahugurwa n'isuzuma rya muganga.
Ubundi buryo bwo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi bugatuma abakozi bumva bamerewe neza. OMS ntidushishikariza kwambara imyenda y'imbere cyangwa y'imbere kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero, idashobora kwandura binyuze mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS itera inkunga gusa kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi ku bakora isuzuma ku binjira.
Ku bantu bafata ibipimo byo guhumeka, kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa kubatwara badafite uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, OMS itera inkunga ko bakoresha udupfukamunwa, indorerwamo zo kurinda, cyangwa inkinzo zo mu maso, amakanzu n'utugati.
Iyo hakozwe igikorwa cyo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa gakoreshwa mu kubaga gasimbuzwa udupfukamunwa twa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose nta bikoresho bihagije bya APD bihari, OMS irasaba kugabanya ibisabwa mu bikoresho by'ubuvuzi binyuze mu serivisi z'ubuvuzi z'uruhande, kugabanya imipaka y'umubiri nko mu madirishya y'ubwirinzi, abantu bakora mu buvuzi bw'imanza gusa ni bo bemerewe kwinjira mu cyumba kirimo abarwayi ba COVID-19, bakoresha gusa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bikenewe mu kazi runaka, bakomeza gukoresha ibikoresho bimwe by'ubuvuzi badacika mu gihe bavura abarwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza uruziga rw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, no kudashishikariza abantu batagira ibimenyetso gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
