Katherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, na Tony S), n'abandi bagize itsinda ry'ubuyobozi (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M, na Toby N).
b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzymes iba ku gice cy'inyuma cy'ingirabuzimafatizo (urwihingiro rw'ingirabuzimafatizo) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 igira ibikorwa bitandukanye n'iby'indwara ya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE), igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II kandi igatuma angiotensin (1-7) yiyongera, bityo ikaba ikora nk'intego y'imiti yizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'ahantu ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe.
ACE2 zigize umuntu zikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Ingingo z'ingenzi mu gutuma amaraso ahinduka ingirabuzima fatizo 2 ni ingirabuzima fatizo zirimo zinge ziri ku gice cy'umubiri w'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite M2 peptidase domain-N-terminal na domain ya transporter ya acide amino ya renal collectrin-C-terminal.
ACE2 ni poroteyine imwe y'uruhu rwa membrane y'ubwoko bwa I, ifite urubuga rw'ingenzi ku buryo bwa enzymatic ku mibiri y'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibice by'ibindi.
Uruhare rwa ACE2 rwo mu rwego rwa extracellular rutandukanywa n'uruhande rw'urundi rugingo rwa transmembrane n'indi ngirabuzima, izwi nka sheddase, maze poroteyine itavamo ikurwa mu maraso, amaherezo igashyirwa mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyane cyane imyanya y'ubuhumekero ya alveolar type II, enterocyte zo mu nda ntoya, ingirabuzimafatizo z'imitsi y'amaraso n'imyanya y'amaraso, n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umusatsi w'amaraso mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Igikorwa cya mRNA ACE2 cyanabonetse mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, n'ubwonko bw'ubwonko.
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwa ACE2 ni ugusigasira ACE.
ACE isenya igipimo cya angiotensin I mu gihe angiotensin II ikora nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso.
Amaherezo, ACE2 yagabanyije amino acide phenylalanine terminal carboxyl ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze iyisimbuza angiotensin (1-7) ikora vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no gusenya izindi peptides nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itegeka uruhu rw'uruhu rw'umunyamideli utwara amino acide SLC6A19 kandi igira uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari poroteyine itera udutsi tw'amaraso, ikora nk'ahantu h'ibanze habonekera virusi zimwe na zimwe za koronavirusi, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine S1 mu byuma bya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 na ACE2 ku rwego rwa selile bituma virusi n'indwara zisohoka mu mubiri.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira muri virusi kandi isaba priming ya poroteyine S na serine protease TMPRSS2, ubu ikumira ryayo ririmo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora gufasha.
Ariko, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe amategeko zisaba gukomeza gukoresha ACE inhibitors na ARB standard.
Isesengura ryakozwe mu buryo buhoraho n'isesengura ryakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, ryagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byateje igabanuka rikomeye rya 34% mu byago bya pneumonia ugereranyije n'abatabifite".
Ikindi kandi, "gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byagabanyije ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane mu barwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara ibicurane, cyane cyane abarwayi bafite indwara y'ibicurane n'umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byatewe no kugabanya impfu ziterwa na Pneumonia, nubwo ingaruka zabyo zari nke ugereranyije n'ibyago byo kurwara Pneumonia muri rusange".
ACE2 y'umuntu ikora (rhACE2) yitezweho kuba uburyo bushya bwo kuvura ibikomere by'ibihaha, kandi bisa nkaho byongera haemodynamics y'ibihaha na oxygen saturation mu bana b'ingurube bafite indwara y'ibihaha ikururwa na lipoplysaride.
Igihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina hagati y'abantu n'inyamaswa ni amasaha 10 n'iminota 30 kandi ingaruka zayo zimara amasaha 24.
Bimwe mu byatahuwe bigaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti utera icyizere ku barwayi batemera ibiyobyabwenge bya RAS (Renin-angiotensin system inhibitors) cyangwa se ku barwayi bafite angiotensin II mu maraso.
b'Iporogaramu ya COVID-19 ni porogaramu ya porogaramu igendanwa yagenewe gufasha gukurikirana abantu mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'abantu banduye.
Hari porogaramu nyinshi zikorwa cyangwa zigezweho, zishimangirwa na leta mu turere dutandukanye no mu nzego zimwe na zimwe.
Imyubakire itandukanye yo kubaka porogaramu yo gukurikirana abakundana yarakozwe.
Ikibazo cy'ibanga kirakemurwa, cyane cyane ku bijyanye na sisitemu ishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Ibindi byagufasha kwirinda guhungabanya ubuzima bwite bwawe harimo gukoresha Bluetooth mu kwandika aho uri n'ibindi byuma bya telefoni.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bagiye gushyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu y'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barigeze guhura n'abantu barwaye COVID-19.
Ni porogaramu ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo mu karere, yasohotse nk'isoko ryuguruye kandi izashyikirizwa leta.
Ni porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu iracyategereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu byiciro by'iterambere kandi ko izaba iboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'izo ziteganyijwe muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande zirimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether yo muri Singapuru na BlueTrace protocol. Uburusiya bufite intego yo gushyiraho porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi basanzwemo COVID-19 baba i Moscou; iyi porogaramu yagenewe kubahiriza ko batagenda.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubushakashatsi mu by'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, avuga ibibazo byinshi by'ingirakamaro bishobora kubaho ku buryo bushingiye ku bikoresho, birimo ibyiza by'ibinyoma n'ubushobozi buke bushoboka iyo amakuru yakiriwe na porogaramu agenewe igice gito cy'abaturage gusa.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira rya porogaramu za "coronavirus" z'ikinyoma cyangwa zangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongera porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus muri App Store, igahagarika gusa imiryango "yemewe" cyangwa ifite izina ryiza.
Google na Amazon bashyiraho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikira ubuzima bwite bw'abantu bagaragaje impungenge bafite ku ngaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi ku bwinshi bikoreshwa na porogaramu za coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizahagarikwa igihe icyorezo kizaba kimaze guhita.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura buhagarikwa.
Iri shyirahamwe ryashyizeho ibintu umunani bisabwa ku mishinga ya leta:
kugenzura bigomba kuba "bikwiye, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'amategeko";
kwagura igenzura n'igenzura bigomba kugira ingingo y'izuba rirenze;
gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba mu rwego rwo kwirinda COVID-19;
umutekano n'ubwisungane mu gutanga amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bigomba kugaragara ko birindwa bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda ivangura n'amacakubiri;
gusangira amakuru n'abantu batatu bigomba kuba byarateganyijwe n'amategeko;
hagomba kubaho uburinzi ku ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo gusubiza ihohoterwa;
Kwitabira by'umwihariko "abafite aho babogamiye bose" ni ngombwa, biganjemo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'itsinda ry'abantu batagira aho babogamira.
Umugambi uteganyijwe wa Google/Apple ugamije gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi buhoraho mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana muri sisitemu y'imikorere y'ibikoresho iyo bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bikoresha uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari hakoreshejwe urubuga, aho gukoresha porogaramu, bityo bikirinda ko hakenerwa gukuramo porogaramu no kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, gukurikirana hakoreshejwe imiyoboro y'ikoranabuhanga byemewe.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite ibyangombwa by'aho umuntu ari bihari bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru zikeneye kubona amakuru yihariye yerekeye ahantu; hari sisitemu zimwe na zimwe zirinda ubuzima bwite zashyizweho kandi zikoresha seriveri nkuru gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshwa uburyo butari bushingiye ku porogaramu bwo gukurikirana abakoraho.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu ikusanya amakuru yo gukurikirana mu bitangazamakuru bitandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya telefoni na karita y'ubucuruzi, kandi ikomatanya aya makuru kugirango itange imenyesha binyuze mu butumwa bugufi ku bantu bashobora kwandura.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo aburire abantu bashobora kuba baragize aho bahurira, leta yashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'aho umuntu aherereye, ibyo bikaba byaratumye hashyirwaho amategeko y'ibanga nyuma y'aho iki cyorezo cy'indwara ya MERS kigaragaye mu gihugu.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na website. Ibihugu nk'u Budage birimo gutekereza gukoresha uburyo bwigenga kandi bukingira ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza tariki ya 6 Mata 2020, ntabwo amakuru aratangazwa.
Kurikirana guhura n'abantu birinda ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyashyizweho, hamwe n'ubutumwa bwinshi bw'ubushakashatsi butangirira nibura mu 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'abahanga barimo gukora ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nk'ikoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE), kugira ngo bandike aho abakoresha begereye izindi terefone.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni umuhate wo guhuza ibintu ukubiyemo uburyo bwigenga kandi butari bumwe, aho kuba protocol imwe. Protocol ziterwa n'ubwitange zirimo: Gukurikirana kwegereyeho kurinda ubuzima bwite bw'abantu (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Impapuro z'igihe gito (TCN, mbere yitwaga Impapuro z'ibyabaye mu guhura, CEN), Protocol na Mechanism yumvikana mu bwisanzure bwo gukurikirana ububiko bw'ibikoresho (PACT), n'ibindi.
Muri iyi protocol, amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye atajya ava ku gikoresho, kandi guhuza byose bibera ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga rya MIT Media Lab ryatangije SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukoresha ubuhanga burinda ubuzima bwite mu gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari cyangwa aho avana amakuru kugira ngo akurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Byashingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'igitabo cy'umweru "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ikindi kigeragezo gisa ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace na Enigma MPC, isosiyete ikora ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga kandi yari yashinzwe na MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bifite umutekano kugira ngo abasoresha bashobore gusangira aho bari n'amakuru y'ubuzima bufite ibisobanuro ku bandi bakoresha n'abakozi batagomba guhungabanya ubuzima bwite bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Inteko mpuzamahanga y'abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga yashyizweho n'amatsinda afite uburyo bumwe kandi ni protocol nyinshi zisabana, hagamijwe kugabanya icyuho no gutuma habaho ubufatanye ku isi hose ku bikoresho byo gukurikirana no kugabisha, ari nabyo bintu by'ingenzi mu kugera ku kwemerwa cyane.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize ku isoko rya BlueTrace protocol ikoreshwa na porogaramu zemewe na guverinoma yayo.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura imbuga ngendanwa za Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakora, bavuga ko bizarinda ubuzima bwite, bishingiye ku buryo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth y'ingufu nke n'ibanga ry'ibanga.
Nanone kandi, basohoye ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanze rikoreshwa muri iyo gahunda.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi gahunda igomba gutangira mu byiciro bitatu:
gutangiza igikoresho cyo kwemerera leta gukora porogaramu zemewe zo gukurikirana coronavirus zirinda ubuzima bwite
Google na Apple bateganya gukemura ikibazo cyo gukusanya amakuru no kugenzura buri gihe mu kubanza gutanga sisitemu binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu y'imikorere, hanyuma bakayikuramo muri ubwo buryo nyuma y'uko iterabwoba rirangiye.
b'Igikorwa cyo guhindura imiti (cyitwa kandi gutanga intego nshya, imiterere mishya, cyangwa inshingano nshya ku muti cyangwa guhindura uburyo bwo kuvura) ni ugukoresha umuti wemewe ku muti mushya, ku ndwara cyangwa ku mimerere y'ubuzima itandukanye n'intego y'ibanze yo gukora umuti.
Ubu buryo ni bwo bushakashatsi bwa siyansi bukomeje gukorwa mu rwego rwo gukora imiti ya COVID-19 ifite umutekano kandi igira ingaruka nziza.
Ibindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi birimo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa amaraso ya plasma. SARS-CoV-2 ifite za poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora kuba intego y'imiti, buri poroteyine ifite ahantu henshi hafatira ligands.
Isesengura ry'ibyo bice by'uruhu bishobora kuba ishingiro ry'umushinga wo gukora imiti ya virusi ikoreshwa cyane mu kurinda za poroteyine za COVID-19.
Bimwe mu byuma by'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 ikoresha ni protease ya papain, RNA polymerase ihagarariye-RNA, helikase, protein S, na ADP ribophosphatease.
Hussein A A, et al basuzumye zimwe mu nzego z'ibanze z'ibanze z'ibanze, hanyuma bazisubiramo maze basuzuma uko zisa n'imiti yemewe kandi ifite ubushobozi bwo kwihutisha iterambere ry'imiti ya SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bw'ibanze kugira ngo zisabwe mu bushakashatsi bw'imiti.
Klorokuin ni umuti wa antimalariya ukoreshwa no mu kurwanya indwara zimwe na zimwe z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydrochloroquine bifitanye isano ari bibiri mu miti ine izigwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rya Solidarity.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo, yatangaje ko igeragezwa rya chloroquine na hydrochlorothiazine muri New York rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate hashingiwe ku Burenganzira bwo Gukoresha Ibiza (USA).
Iyi miti ntabwo yemejwe na FDA mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi kandi yemejwe ku buryo bwa EUA gusa nk'umuti w'igerageza wo gukoresha byihuse mu barwayi bari mu bitaro, ariko badashobora kwakira imiti mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
CDC ivuga ko "imikoreshereze, dosiye cyangwa igihe hydroxychloroquine ikoreshwa mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2" itarashyirwaho.
Abaganga bavuga ko bakoresha iyo miti mu gihe "nta kundi babigenza".
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya bo muri Istanbul barimo barakora ubushakashatsi buto ku bihereranye no gukoresha chloroquine ivanze na zingu, vitamini A, vitamini C na vitamini D.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye burakomeje muri kaminuza ya Duke na Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo gukora igerageza ku mutekano n'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukoresha hydroxychloroquine.
Ibizamini byo mu Bushinwa byabereye i Wuhan no mu mujyi wa Shenzhen byavuze ko favipiravir yagaragaye ko "ifite ubushobozi".
Abarwayi 35 bo mu mujyi wa Shenzhen bagaragaje ko nta muti wabakiriye mu gihe cy'iminsi 4, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batakiriye uwo muti bagaragaje ko bamaze iminsi 11.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye ibicurane by'amahembe, kimwe cya kabiri cy'abarwayi bahawe favipiravir, ikindi kimwe cya kabiri bahabwa umifenovir.
