Nk'uko bivugwa na South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yashyikirije Trump gahunda yo kugura uwo muti ushobora kuba udafite akamaro mu gihe cy'indwara ikomeye y'agakoko kayanduza abantu benshi.
Iyi miti ishobora kuba atari myiza ku mugore utwite cyangwa ku muntu ugerageza gusama.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kuri lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), ari byo bikoresho bikoresha imiti ya lopinavir na ritonavir, bwagaragaje ko nta nyungu zabyo zagaragaye.
Iyi miti yagenewe kubuza virusi itera SIDA kongera kwiyongera binyuze mu guhuza protease.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Colorado barimo baragerageza guhindura imiti kugira ngo babone ikinyabutabire kiyihuza na protease ya SARS-CoV-2. Hariho kunenga mu muryango w'abahanga ku bijyanye no gushyira umutungo mu mishinga y'imiti yakozwe by'umwihariko kuri HIV/AIDS.
OMS yashyize lopinavir/ritonavir mu igerageza mpuzamahanga rya Solidarity.
Remdesivir yakozwe kandi iterwa imbere na Gilead Sciences nk'umuti w'indwara ya Ebola na Marburg virus infection. Nyuma, Gilead Sciences yaje kubona ko Remdesivir ifite ibikorwa bya antiviral in vitro kuri zimwe muri phyllo-, pneumo-, paramikso-, na coronaviruses.
Kimwe mu bibazo by'imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara ni uko ishobora gutera indwara no kuyandura kurushaho.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu igerageza rya mbere bwagaragaje ko remdesivir ishobora kugira inzitizi ikomeye mu buryo bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima. Hariho ibigeragezo byinshi biri gukorwa, birimo ibigeragezo bibiri byakozwe n'ibitaro bya Kaminuza ya Cleveland, kimwe ku bantu barwaye indwara yoroheje ikindi ku bantu barwaye cyane.
Hari ibizamini bitatu byo kwa muganga birimo gukorwa ku bantu barwariye mu bitaro kandi barwaye COVID-19 cyane, bibiri ni ibipimo bya placebo (Ubushinwa, Kanada) n'ikindi kimwe ni ibyo kutagira ibipimo (Ubutariyani).
