Abashakashatsi bo mu kigo cy'umutima cya Montreal muri Canada barimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku ruhare rwa kolkisine mu kugabanya ubuhumekero n'ibibazo by'ibihaha mu barwayi barwaye COVID-19 bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwiswe COLCORONA, bwitabiriwe n'abantu bakuru 6000 bafite imyaka 40 kuzamura basanganywe COVID-19 kandi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje ku buryo batagombaga kujya mu bitaro.
