Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo byinshi ku barwayi 300 bugenzura gukoresha enoxaparin sodium mu buryo bwo kwirinda no kuvura, bwatangajwe mu Butaliyani ku ya 14 Mata.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi, ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwibanze ku gutanga imiti mishya ku miti ya virusi yemewe kandi yakozwe mu ndwara z'ibyorezo byabanje, nka MERS, SARS, na virusi ya West Nile.
