Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko, nk'uko WHO ibivuga, urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi itera iyi ndwara, rutazaba ruboneka mu gihe kitarenze amezi 18.
Inkingo eshanu z'abakandida ziri mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi bw'umutekano muri Mata.
COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu Kuboza 2019.
Icyorezo gikomeye cyakwirakwiriye ku isi yose mu mwaka wa 2020, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga menshi n'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi mu gukora urukingo.
Imiryango myinshi ikoresha genomes zashyizwe ahagaragara mu gukora inkingo zishobora kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Umushinga wa CEPI watanze itangazo muri Mata ko ibintu by'ingenzi mu gukora urukingo ari umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, gukwirakwiza ku kigero gikenewe, ndetse no kugera ku isi yose.
Muri Mata, abahanga muri CEPI batangaje ko ibigo 10 bitandukanye by'ikoranabuhanga biri mu bushakashatsi no mu iterambere mu ntangiriro za 2020 mu gukora urukingo rukora neza kuri COVID-19.
Intego nyamukuru z'ibigo byateye imbere mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi ku mutekano, harimo:
aside ya nucleate (DNA na RNA) (abakoze icyiciro cya mbere n'abakandida b'urukingo: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virusi (abakoze icyiciro cya mbere n'urukingo rw'umukandida: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus ya virusi y'ubwoko bwa 5)
Nk'uko byavuzwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI muri Mata, abakandida 115 b'inkingo bari mu byiciro bya mbere by'iterambere, aho 78 byemejwe ko ari imishinga ikora (79, nk'uko ikigo Milken Institute kibivuga), n'abandi 37 batangajwe, ariko hari amakuru make y'abaturage (bafatwa nk'abategura cyangwa bateguye).
Ibizamini byo mu cyiciro cya mbere n'icya kabiri bigira igerageza ry'umutekano n'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara, akenshi bikorerwa mu buryo butunguranye, bigenzurwa na placebo, kandi mu duce dutandukanye, mu gihe hashyirwaho dosiye ikora neza.
Ibizamini bya Phase III bikunze kuba birimo abitabiriye benshi, harimo n'itsinda ry'abashinzwe kugenzura, kandi bikagerageza ubushobozi bw'urukingo mu gukumira indwara, mu gihe hagenzurwa ingaruka mbi ku gipimo cyiza.
Mu bakandida 79 b'inkingo bari mu bikorwa byo gukora (bemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 muri bo ntibaragera mu igeragezwa ku bantu (baracyari mu bushakashatsi "bw'imbere y'ivuriro").
