Inkingo z'igerageza zakozwe hakoreshejwe izo ngamba zigomba kugeragezwa kugira ngo hamenyekane umutekano n'ubushobozi bwazo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangiranye n'abakorerabushake bane i Seattle.
Inkingo zirimo kode y'imiterere idahumanye yakuwe muri virusi iteza indwara. Kwiyongera kw'abashingiye ku bisimba by'abanduye byatanzwe nk'ikibazo gishobora kuvugwa mu iterambere ry'inkingo za SARS-COV-2, ariko ubu buryo buracyari impaka.
Hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumye imiti yemewe ya malaria, harimo ibyiciro bine by'ibizamini bya hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti mishya ya antiviral igizwe n'ibice byinshi by'ubushakashatsi bw'u Bushinwa, hamwe n'ibice icyenda by'igerageza rya Remdesivir mu bihugu bitandukanye, aho igihe ntarengwa cyo gutanga raporo kiri mu mpera za Mata.
Muri Mata 2020, hari igenzura rikomeye ry'iterambere mu buvuzi ry'urukingo n'imiti ya COVID-19. Hari imiti ya virusi iri gukorwa mu rwego rwo kuvura COVID-19, irimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo by'uko remdesivir igira ingaruka nziza.
Iterambere mu buvuzi ryagaragaye mu barwayi bahabwa remdesivir mu buvuzi bw'imiti itagoranye.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya III birakorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, yari isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malaria, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, igatanga umusaruro w'ibanze.
Nyamara, hari hakenewe ko ibyo byigwa bisubirwamo n'abandi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'igihugu cya Koreya n'ubw'Ubushinwa bwemeje gukoresha chlorokuine.
Icyakora, Ikigo cya Wuhan cya Virology, nubwo gitanga urugero rw'igarama imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko iyo mirwi ibiri ari mibi cyane kandi ishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku buryo bw'ubuvuzi ku baganga bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'Ubushinwa yo ku ncuro ya 7 nayo arimo interféron, ribavirin, cyangwa umifenovir yo gukoresha mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko dosiye nyinshi za ribavirin ari ngombwa mu gukumira SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba.
Nitasozanide yasabwe mu bindi byigwa muri in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu rugero rwo hasi. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutangira mbere kuri poroteyine y'ibinure na serine protease transmembrane 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa cyane kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhura n'urwungano rw'urwungano rwa ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi kuri chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite izo ngaruka bufite aho bugarukira cyane byatumye umuryango w'abaganga utabikoresha nta bushakashatsi bwuzuye. Oseltamivir ntibuza SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba kandi nta ruhare ruzwi mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibibazo by'inkubi y'umuyaga wa sitokine bishobora kubaho mu gihe COVID-19 imaze igihe kirekire.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imiterere ya antisytocins. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'imiti na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'Ubushinwa nyuma y'uko isuzuma rito ryarangiye.
Uyu muti uri mu igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya kabiri mu gihugu cyose mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza umusaruro mwiza ku bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Iyo bifatanyije n'ibizamini by'amaraso ya feritini ya serum kugira ngo bamenye ibiza bya sitokine, iyo miti iba igamije kurwanya ibiza bya sitokine, bikekwa ko ari byo bituma abantu bamwe na bamwe bibasirwa n'ibiza bihitana.
Mu 2017, interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yemejwe na FDA ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bw'imyanzuro y'ibanze ku miti ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara y'indwara ya sitokine ituma abarwayi ba steroid batakaza amaraso bitewe n'impamvu zitandukanye, ari yo CAR T cell therapy.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya ihamye kandi iteganyijwe igaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
